pener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjNdI98ctJgB65tkekyOx0pFhR2tZ5B6-NhTkoS0gjSmg2ejTAqI2jy6nKm8ojFtza1q9ddFgmWXHPqs6auDwn2SvOUWy3TbWf1LXYh2hZl0AtgtSUhlh-uYybyKeJ5gDb-C5WWex_cXLrwNV0l9O52GIshXriv1_F1m47bVmqIq37GpN4CYxv6oyDmI14/s600/DSC05236.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲近拍一張讓大家看一下翻譯，我是覺得蠻ＯＫ的</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEg4KIWoI4lOo_k2AnOoPWMJ7A9dQ0H5fjSti-7cja32vlorm-Xgh2ATr7v4mDQqGDnxcdxDXgXLXvhoXXjBpGnY2T5kIJ9bQbYnh0VgDCpXs4a91e4GVZLhH52qRGYw2tsByHwxmTPnvWEybdkj0oqAHsDuh0zIuFiTe3vtHx21etWv2rwirbHL_Abh1mg/s4696/DSC05237.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEg4KIWoI4lOo_k2AnOoPWMJ7A9dQ0H5fjSti-7cja32vlorm-Xgh2ATr7v4mDQqGDnxcdxDXgXLXvhoXXjBpGnY2T5kIJ9bQbYnh0VgDCpXs4a91e4GVZLhH52qRGYw2tsByHwxmTPnvWEybdkj0oqAHsDuh0zIuFiTe3vtHx21etWv2rwirbHL_Abh1mg/s600/DSC05237.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲員工卡，有各式各樣的員工可以聘請</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEi31S-02oUb8G93ekkJMuRErBc_TfI8HO0wngpA9QASC6N7BcRkelgmSYgcNAkVgp4EoNwkTHLmyTpfK8S22KcaFU6Ek7mM_VTmOTOpxlg0XD5pznnGZO9dLS8u80k-bjjcz1QpQyLAJeNERcXbbif8O-aWdQjQaIqPtjxckqo_G5yVVPozHrolrxucVPI/s4236/DSC05238.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEi31S-02oUb8G93ekkJMuRErBc_TfI8HO0wngpA9QASC6N7BcRkelgmSYgcNAkVgp4EoNwkTHLmyTpfK8S22KcaFU6Ek7mM_VTmOTOpxlg0XD5pznnGZO9dLS8u80k-bjjcz1QpQyLAJeNERcXbbif8O-aWdQjQaIqPtjxckqo_G5yVVPozHrolrxucVPI/s600/DSC05238.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲ＡＩ卡，單人遊玩的好夥伴～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEhBx-G6vQ1JfRrmM-RfLiBMjyxnwdPt6KUGl_AuCNrOuqaEFstj21MBm63FB4O_V75-9LYQmyj32VT93TvdItw4e__XbxxzkOKPNyrkCFMlJjR5za2Un0p7FgfZteu043VoyOX3oSYAvLLYRhxW4xMMbD2SIJa3g_JoRDtDeCbvrM98tO_4cFLUw6DwNG8\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiZZ4XC21XbhVbBRWe3JyMxlOoTN-B-aPeYC3YYiG6Y1R2uLQvQ1WhXHcZtxPUigeMTXBXmPXOU11XuLLR801AW_iY7S3g89rBLa1nvzDLPQHtGDTu99109tFLRb2u_hv2W6GfvmCeY0iQ7JzJYzCkUyEyCYufjH8Ed5RZG0tITsX8vEgXQRN6LTOcwJS4/w640-h418/DSC05239.JPG\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲每場遊戲會隨機翻出３張設施卡與３張員工卡來設置，遊戲的變化主要就來自這邊～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">遊戲共進行三年，每一年會有兩個準備階段與一個開園階段～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">【準備階段】</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">會隨機抽出玩家人數＋１的骰子，投擲之後大家輪流選骰子並獲得骰子上的符號～選骰子的順序為ＡＢＣＣＢＡ這樣的方式～最後剩下的那顆骰子上的符號所有人都能獲得～但是，也必須同時獲得該骰子上面的危險點數～（前面自選骰子上的危險點數不用看）</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">所有人都拿到骰子之後，開始進行骰子工放，將骰子放到中央圖板當中的格子並執行行動～可以做的行動有：（１）製造最多４隻恐龍（２）拿錢／或是拿安全鎖（３）拿兩個基本DNA／或是一個高級DNA（４）拿兩倍該骰子上的資源＆其他玩家拿一倍（５）蓋三條路／或是蓋一座園區設施。</p><p><br></p><p>都執行之後起始玩家照順位換人～</p><p><br></p><p>【開園階段】</p><p>這個階段共有五個步驟，一步一步來：</p><p>（１）景點：園區內有蓋設施的，此時會帶你給好處（順序自選）</p><p>（２）專家：六名可雇用的員工會在此時工作（順序自選）</p><p>（３）恐龍之旅：從總部開始導覽遊客進入你的公園並從出口離開（每個第一次遇到的建築會提供一點興奮值），有被使用到的出口，遊戲結束時會提供分數。</p><p>（４）興奮值：根據目前得到的興奮值來拿獎勵～（前幾年累積的也會再次拿獎勵）</p><p>（５）死亡人數：如果你的安全鎖追不上你的危險等級，那公園內就會發生不幸～你也會得到相對應的懲罰～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhx2yz4bYgJcQ0ENBMZyamQ6yhfvH0i4Eg1bv7cwM6kKo5gkZevHwwcqjqr83e92b7Bes3s8i49u8hY97X8OA5PL1_SUV9Ar0rrhf4JsPXvFfzjuS9WTfM0o9LE7nznknCpBV8Kpn6LW2Cdr5SBc2BulPZoBSa5b_OB2ndb2Pf9mnDfDY95SQUu3d91zAE/s600/DSC05227.JPG\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲雖然規則有點細～但由於圖示很清楚，所以玩起來不難～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">這款遊戲我就是被桌遊怪的影片給推坑的，因此很推薦大家看：</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲基本規則教學＋遊玩前半</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲實際遊戲遊玩延伸</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲遊戲心得評測</p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEiYbh5ZNhgL3QWxTiO9ZKf4jv95tgiXvjsaqGl30jCUqgwJyk5onnPX739IRgNXS69jmtVDTGwDWXaylhxyYz2shhCchboJrExzfnllNXFseSKo2uc14FU7HKZ3gx9uF0HoIQgkny2zOFODXOOC4lD2Wx7Fdlqg2SPdgwHqkSh97Sb61LhZFVTUuHq0aVI\"></p><p><br></p><p>比<strong>主遊戲好玩～</strong></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">骰寫版的遊戲何其多，大部分都是提供大家好攜帶，或是遊戲時間短，遊戲難度下降等等的好處～但真要舉一款骰寫遊戲可以超越主遊戲的，我暫時是想不出來～但！《Dinosaur Island Rawr’n Write 骰筆恐龍島》帶給我的遊戲體驗，我覺得是不輸給主遊戲的～甚至我可能要很久很久才有力氣開一場《恐龍島》，而《Dinosaur Island Rawr’n Write 骰筆恐龍島》應該會讓我最近蠻想常常拿出來玩的～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">這款遊戲在恐龍之旅階段有用到一筆畫的概念，這個時候就不得不跟大家推薦一款免費的紙筆遊戲<a href=\"https://usnoopy.blogspot.com/2019/04/dino-land-p.html\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">【免費玩桌遊】恐龍樂園 Dino Land P&amp;P 免費下載</a>。這是我幾年前做的一款免費桌遊，還沒玩過的朋友可以試玩看看喔～</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEg9n5VIYz-nFoojLKcMxdHp9oZlJ3EW3-X88Dma8FPuZDAWU43j6n4ZQzozBT2HwjejTygkZhD8242vXxvShBQAiavq-ntrEwKAw_0cYBXRkb1KzgG36Nz9YeIdnyLbxhOSR72FGDrIQlmw1UGjXvEIb3drfFUozCJNVwOO_ISnKvJoJJzkAKVxi1TREog/s4544/DSC05240.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEg9n5VIYz-nFoojLKcMxdHp9oZlJ3EW3-X88Dma8FPuZDAWU43j6n4ZQzozBT2HwjejTygkZhD8242vXxvShBQAiavq-ntrEwKAw_0cYBXRkb1KzgG36Nz9YeIdnyLbxhOSR72FGDrIQlmw1UGjXvEIb3drfFUozCJNVwOO_ISnKvJoJJzkAKVxi1TREog/s600/DSC05240.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲遊戲收納照</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjwU6Ovm3oBSHt7XHAaIzGbTHuqaadBnJYbYm5_0IJ_DoW9RmRFucdvkZFFDsQaHUIUAee9tRsT3VBMVinPlzS5nEynPB2Oau5nRtJUZzHCN_SMKWBMQ_Et66XUwbTNkt56fdH-wZw1fDTspcM-0RX9ncDRt5klym0gav8h6pEI1ImQ9PO2Kop5ma5k1GY/w640-h296/20240714_224741(0).jpg\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲玩這種紙筆遊戲很多的樂趣也來自塗鴉，跟大家分享家中小朋友的畫作～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgTIuYJok_GA6WdWCN4p3VNbWt_yxR1fTyiqqIDTLgj7tjxr9MflyGFSZzy6Ej4QBRWV5YDXW0FD1PpG4SpmvAmpAb3BqyhyphenhyphenA39ZcS-wPOmAydaRj8F2t3QPxt0u1TUQNVB1u8ibtzwpQ-IdQxh4g4R_KQ_DcIDWEoNb4DIFHkpVmiylhtqmyZ_sDD2k6s/s4904/DSC05232.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgTIuYJok_GA6WdWCN4p3VNbWt_yxR1fTyiqqIDTLgj7tjxr9MflyGFSZzy6Ej4QBRWV5YDXW0FD1PpG4SpmvAmpAb3BqyhyphenhyphenA39ZcS-wPOmAydaRj8F2t3QPxt0u1TUQNVB1u8ibtzwpQ-IdQxh4g4R_KQ_DcIDWEoNb4DIFHkpVmiylhtqmyZ_sDD2k6s/s600/DSC05232.JPG\"></a></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p>', '2024-11-18 09:45:22', '2024-11-18 09:45:22', 1, 'forum-1731894322310-279233037.jpg');
INSERT INTO `forum_posts` (`id`, `user_id`, `title`, `content`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `status`, `cover_image`) VALUES
(12, 1, '【桌遊開箱報】奧茲國 冒險之路 《綠野仙蹤》 開箱+介紹', '<h3><br></h3><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh6Vf_7p0m1Gc3n3S9dDnhOtY_6dCId7eTvJmp_jq4WLwM8tIsnlrobtempaTRDJ6htJ6ugCvXL6eGm9wAewNOBSHSaXyrCQSgRIu7xpgXwM8bu1eF559AqaONKJ2m7nFzjaJHut-iVM4ypmzq65QYfzIj0q1hgWBfnUkXfAmk119IopkGB1xsChVpf1To/s3372/DSC05078.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh6Vf_7p0m1Gc3n3S9dDnhOtY_6dCId7eTvJmp_jq4WLwM8tIsnlrobtempaTRDJ6htJ6ugCvXL6eGm9wAewNOBSHSaXyrCQSgRIu7xpgXwM8bu1eF559AqaONKJ2m7nFzjaJHut-iVM4ypmzq65QYfzIj0q1hgWBfnUkXfAmk119IopkGB1xsChVpf1To/s600/DSC05078.JPG\"></a></p><p><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEhv2DiXmQzC9J3Fr9bACz2Zcw39buqwMoqeTvtk2F02DLUyoftW_hbKIj4qipKykCm3inKZ_0dE4MIEWjrmI1wxrBz5n_czLfcKo6WiTcN572F9C0zDBljpqMVr3jTZmTsmRL2T81fTlcLQqcZVy6qzpspnJkDfscqvL4wUuGcuVzIml2Qjfe2LosMgU0o\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">『我做了一個夢，我去遊歷～經歷多麼危險又有趣～小獅王和機器人和稻草人，都是我的好伙計。我的小狗叫托托，他也一起去～』這些歌詞都是我上網查來的，我一個字也不會唱，更別說我絕對不知道托托那一段歌詞後面還有很可愛的狗叫聲，我是不可能會知道的～（逃走）</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">《綠野仙蹤》對小時候的我是很神奇的存在，龍捲風、看不到盡頭的黃色道路、可愛的夥伴們、以及奧茲王國～幾年前我還買了一本很漂亮的立體書，翻開的第一頁就是可以轉動的龍捲風～還有附綠色的眼鏡可以看立體的奧茲城堡～因此對於這次的《綠野仙蹤》遊戲與故事書，我期待值其實是拉得很高的！</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲很懷念的主題曲還有片頭</p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEh4k4vF8_6OaIXoWDX2uMflZtcp1Csa4sdq7OZpqlgDr5WVvqtFif0jJrFDTPhAxUGJiFtOALCd7Ed-Y-XyW_b78vP582EJEfkzfPdALAqwoO-irtnm3ordBJXEFJW4ESvS1QFDuKVBebvAfzfIizrDOAqE4v_ELfIivvW9GclB53gx3JW6RGbVJMWxpb0\"></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhvykGAnubE93agwW6NZ-lyk_5xpgkzIEsSFqmmGGnE9MdVksRUfQGmlqG057gJRPl6PuHakhwzC1QuF76PElXByMdlhVdT00-upOGaMo-ySEY-Rdj7rnvZjXVAnbWPZCIX5D8nweZW_PKJHbx5vC99Khj3XI7OXGacWZuCElIMH3_Vko1MqMS1GEmanpY/s5148/DSC05079.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhvykGAnubE93agwW6NZ-lyk_5xpgkzIEsSFqmmGGnE9MdVksRUfQGmlqG057gJRPl6PuHakhwzC1QuF76PElXByMdlhVdT00-upOGaMo-ySEY-Rdj7rnvZjXVAnbWPZCIX5D8nweZW_PKJHbx5vC99Khj3XI7OXGacWZuCElIMH3_Vko1MqMS1GEmanpY/s600/DSC05079.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲這次除了桌遊之外，還有一本故事書，特殊色子（紙）跟主角群的磁鐵</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEij2PPBA4ZCIhrAvIU4i15yhHIV7k2Rezqu640dQxWAnBrpMYH0OJ945U1ykAh2lK_NVckPCuZTKalED1Md5Ig4L_mw8Bk65dnTaOxa1Ghh9EqcBfUQw4ph5wBBY32r3_G2DaeuZuo_wNAq9BppWR45oXPAI0cxi4lliB3I5anHPqZeYRfcZaLSbd_lWZA/s3924/DSC05080.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEij2PPBA4ZCIhrAvIU4i15yhHIV7k2Rezqu640dQxWAnBrpMYH0OJ945U1ykAh2lK_NVckPCuZTKalED1Md5Ig4L_mw8Bk65dnTaOxa1Ghh9EqcBfUQw4ph5wBBY32r3_G2DaeuZuo_wNAq9BppWR45oXPAI0cxi4lliB3I5anHPqZeYRfcZaLSbd_lWZA/s600/DSC05080.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲遊戲人數：2-4人　建議年齡：10+　遊戲時間：30mins</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEj5Mvgufo-HO_7aWhAPgU62aRVFRZ3R2xEI9fVCXzmiK4F4WnPPqi_kV-2mQgXog1H9TJ_GjGDGWZC0r24wG0wiaRy1cUDKt_sqGJeH1esGnN14m3uVFv_oKpLEzAvG9styoU9bhJORD1CxZdX5MPgizZ493NiwfzkV82qWCZ2i5iSmgywI-5Uo8FDdq5U/s3588/DSC05081.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEj5Mvgufo-HO_7aWhAPgU62aRVFRZ3R2xEI9fVCXzmiK4F4WnPPqi_kV-2mQgXog1H9TJ_GjGDGWZC0r24wG0wiaRy1cUDKt_sqGJeH1esGnN14m3uVFv_oKpLEzAvG9styoU9bhJORD1CxZdX5MPgizZ493NiwfzkV82qWCZ2i5iSmgywI-5Uo8FDdq5U/s600/DSC05081.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲盒底可以看到遊戲概況</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjNoo3Fc9Flder5REkYCB7Cnlm3vBwz3oL4tPSXoYBcbKkb0RJKnNQj7aG9_vkwige61UwwDOvb9bzOqubVeQAa-M72zvwX-hhCMWoriKLBJRru9l6dleNz0BeFCHWkXpGdiHCIz3XZDT_5yjsUs1q_EUK1MeE3pFcxsddWhye0v2elsHHYYwBTu2WNGnE/s3720/DSC05082.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjNoo3Fc9Flder5REkYCB7Cnlm3vBwz3oL4tPSXoYBcbKkb0RJKnNQj7aG9_vkwige61UwwDOvb9bzOqubVeQAa-M72zvwX-hhCMWoriKLBJRru9l6dleNz0BeFCHWkXpGdiHCIz3XZDT_5yjsUs1q_EUK1MeE3pFcxsddWhye0v2elsHHYYwBTu2WNGnE/s600/DSC05082.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲內容物一覽</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhG9VzCxCp12ag7rjJYFOF3ByCwMr68y1mEfwzQuQUoArOuX3cBChu_EQe-1DLRU1e9hKTJ8fqhZGB8WcHQEZvDLXhYIMA59hjMLaf8MqqMj10rBDyU2dAFcrPn7daMCIFZqgeWYz3cOTguicqTiNuSBd3-sgRZFG8ZY1WJlnVHbq_o9YHvNhP7wESvaWk/s4924/DSC05083.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhG9VzCxCp12ag7rjJYFOF3ByCwMr68y1mEfwzQuQUoArOuX3cBChu_EQe-1DLRU1e9hKTJ8fqhZGB8WcHQEZvDLXhYIMA59hjMLaf8MqqMj10rBDyU2dAFcrPn7daMCIFZqgeWYz3cOTguicqTiNuSBd3-sgRZFG8ZY1WJlnVHbq_o9YHvNhP7wESvaWk/s600/DSC05083.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲遊戲地圖是一張雙對折的厚紙</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh5F8nlj9Jh5NGiW-LB_XmlbiaAlFE0711g-5PRzph2XtvFa3F-O8CCZ7syncPoYL9fswHNzhi675Rbv4KmKmQJLCDSxc2bR3dE1KdOQPamC-6Fp46ioteKd4n9E7asNFZdvJjuMbWZp_umZik3BXJxWrAmW0tQB43dR45t0NAdGEQSpJbbWwMYDPWxC1g/s4636/DSC05084.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh5F8nlj9Jh5NGiW-LB_XmlbiaAlFE0711g-5PRzph2XtvFa3F-O8CCZ7syncPoYL9fswHNzhi675Rbv4KmKmQJLCDSxc2bR3dE1KdOQPamC-6Fp46ioteKd4n9E7asNFZdvJjuMbWZp_umZik3BXJxWrAmW0tQB43dR45t0NAdGEQSpJbbWwMYDPWxC1g/s600/DSC05084.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲一顆特殊骰子與各種顏色的棋子</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiHhO5H4NFv8WG8SgUKR_XNnUc9aIWrRbcE-iGsynRVWoCB9i5OWPaQhjB8H1iUr1EK69bHdFyqg6hHASt7TcyBS9r-cC-dj9cmeqXDEUShEy9aHpgJUu39Wvw0Wkf_Jq84TdmfcRj3bNzc_n6dRE1pxMmYBuPI62iGNwYGVDTSZ7Wsecf5K9GjEMtaohc/s4152/DSC05085.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiHhO5H4NFv8WG8SgUKR_XNnUc9aIWrRbcE-iGsynRVWoCB9i5OWPaQhjB8H1iUr1EK69bHdFyqg6hHASt7TcyBS9r-cC-dj9cmeqXDEUShEy9aHpgJUu39Wvw0Wkf_Jq84TdmfcRj3bNzc_n6dRE1pxMmYBuPI62iGNwYGVDTSZ7Wsecf5K9GjEMtaohc/s600/DSC05085.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲卡片一疊</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgRW082ypxPTiu5c5JkVYWz4FqO9Y3bMF-MhSGHXGVYvEZbb6JNn5yYNHv7Ea5MsmYrSjrgj0aI_Nv0w1Xt3XoLk7H9uJw3MGx81TjMSDJcW21IsBlUb9GcZFUVKc2hs1C7Wkvqw5WDvFTKi_whEoz7r_ptopmH-uiw2t2968KbQv-dmmmpEA9JZkNsLk0/s3868/DSC05086.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgRW082ypxPTiu5c5JkVYWz4FqO9Y3bMF-MhSGHXGVYvEZbb6JNn5yYNHv7Ea5MsmYrSjrgj0aI_Nv0w1Xt3XoLk7H9uJw3MGx81TjMSDJcW21IsBlUb9GcZFUVKc2hs1C7Wkvqw5WDvFTKi_whEoz7r_ptopmH-uiw2t2968KbQv-dmmmpEA9JZkNsLk0/s600/DSC05086.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲卡片內容有兩種～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhVUPa-2JXTf20KXgMXq3rywVQq-d0TbzhWNLVbC976I1tiJXehEErv_r7lOcRttx5RSmI1CErtqi1I3fMLxrJLeADBVPY-p8SyIbvPUm5qYR1y8EAsX9V8LBmahO5bHmmMaebHMUA7SK8iTQhMSc_43LIbzYWVGxdRXAK6nj0-q7glob-vbzrTwgwLvjg/s4584/DSC05087.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhVUPa-2JXTf20KXgMXq3rywVQq-d0TbzhWNLVbC976I1tiJXehEErv_r7lOcRttx5RSmI1CErtqi1I3fMLxrJLeADBVPY-p8SyIbvPUm5qYR1y8EAsX9V8LBmahO5bHmmMaebHMUA7SK8iTQhMSc_43LIbzYWVGxdRXAK6nj0-q7glob-vbzrTwgwLvjg/s600/DSC05087.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲粉紅色的卡片是女巫葛林達卡，幫助別人的時候可以獲得～另外也可以用來幫助自己通關～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEj8WYUA1vO9BB35UP6GO1cUbCOxgm54aHL6822pyZuunfXPIef6xdih2wyfq5GYb1RjRwfTEYiLQWAaLOt_jeT4I1YbJ3WI2xWsFdvKu5beuD3ZqGQ8_LtBDByR6L9FH8wUZAjzQ3MMXQVma0QnQLvpoEb1Y2UBlBWl-sZH6rIVfRa3VbWRP7S1pR515YI/s5094/DSC05088.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEj8WYUA1vO9BB35UP6GO1cUbCOxgm54aHL6822pyZuunfXPIef6xdih2wyfq5GYb1RjRwfTEYiLQWAaLOt_jeT4I1YbJ3WI2xWsFdvKu5beuD3ZqGQ8_LtBDByR6L9FH8wUZAjzQ3MMXQVma0QnQLvpoEb1Y2UBlBWl-sZH6rIVfRa3VbWRP7S1pR515YI/s600/DSC05088.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲綠色的卡片又可分為能量卡（左）與怪獸卡（右）</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgbwnb7U7DMueWbhoR3NZm_CmZtPLFXjA-Lj1FH2RmoV-_V0_xKBSNMjcsYKuLKCgS3L14YI1jPt95ls2VOZDDAXaUYiOoG8dVlC4RhGOaPoatBDzWFv191FmjRcB5SuNVw2mBwcdKLtcG59pfn33iATVu_qg9czdTWKk4PxqcMp393A-_TF-d9aMCpq7U/s3704/DSC05089.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgbwnb7U7DMueWbhoR3NZm_CmZtPLFXjA-Lj1FH2RmoV-_V0_xKBSNMjcsYKuLKCgS3L14YI1jPt95ls2VOZDDAXaUYiOoG8dVlC4RhGOaPoatBDzWFv191FmjRcB5SuNVw2mBwcdKLtcG59pfn33iATVu_qg9czdTWKk4PxqcMp393A-_TF-d9aMCpq7U/s600/DSC05089.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲能量卡上的圖案都是從故事書裡面出來的，相當漂亮～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">（上面的點數就是各種能量）</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEhBx-G6vQ1JfRrmM-RfLiBMjyxnwdPt6KUGl_AuCNrOuqaEFstj21MBm63FB4O_V75-9LYQmyj32VT93TvdItw4e__XbxxzkOKPNyrkCFMlJjR5za2Un0p7FgfZteu043VoyOX3oSYAvLLYRhxW4xMMbD2SIJa3g_JoRDtDeCbvrM98tO_4cFLUw6DwNG8\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEj-tyJk7l7KSqsdmSLW99Vj7ewNV-ONotKHT41rdfnLWV8L4ClJdKwFne_lzZ8lC_Jr5z3JTl8d5r2mXHT8sNuQ_-9Gdgg-k8PNwSc9qcn-_pWQzvoEKW1Kilc-1KhFdMnFNuH-zMRsnmW-bPVaaMq00gwUvpOuUsQvclJIW2I54L3diZwGTBMOYe78gzY/s5414/DSC05090.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEj-tyJk7l7KSqsdmSLW99Vj7ewNV-ONotKHT41rdfnLWV8L4ClJdKwFne_lzZ8lC_Jr5z3JTl8d5r2mXHT8sNuQ_-9Gdgg-k8PNwSc9qcn-_pWQzvoEKW1Kilc-1KhFdMnFNuH-zMRsnmW-bPVaaMq00gwUvpOuUsQvclJIW2I54L3diZwGTBMOYe78gzY/s600/DSC05090.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲所有玩家選一個角色，然後從東方蒙奇金出發～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">（顏色我有對照角色放：紅色－小獅子、黃色－錫樵夫、藍色－桃樂絲、綠色－稻草人）</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiM6Lc5879FVQu_stghwTRqjYZIxtFVgKehvEEMGrsq-2LO4So_4uGzauTWNRXXlTU_DLZb2F9-7mjbNTJNfoSC3zpxbllR-7wFT37CHlRhY6selbwIAQVE06VMHUpOSW08cySTpQWhOZj7zLRLqud8XE3b6AZD2M2DVWKCxNlbmKHCda5XCf_QA1Io9W0/s4852/DSC05091.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiM6Lc5879FVQu_stghwTRqjYZIxtFVgKehvEEMGrsq-2LO4So_4uGzauTWNRXXlTU_DLZb2F9-7mjbNTJNfoSC3zpxbllR-7wFT37CHlRhY6selbwIAQVE06VMHUpOSW08cySTpQWhOZj7zLRLqud8XE3b6AZD2M2DVWKCxNlbmKHCda5XCf_QA1Io9W0/s600/DSC05091.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲每位玩家抽取５張卡片</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgdfQm4zE3mbccVdtRw1KcM-72yZ0FhMTCiNcRABvU5cxZhWDr2_l-EbhtPUmV7zgm08uzH4SKNhyHsGSF1o4htEO3zd-ZD2NykTAGwO5cKLCUABQAjhB7lthLQu4TvQBE6UIFZaKpIEXE31pyZQUU-3p5laxlVRWJVtL4qI-xGGHl7v9EHXDHLXo_FC8k/s5108/DSC05092.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgdfQm4zE3mbccVdtRw1KcM-72yZ0FhMTCiNcRABvU5cxZhWDr2_l-EbhtPUmV7zgm08uzH4SKNhyHsGSF1o4htEO3zd-ZD2NykTAGwO5cKLCUABQAjhB7lthLQu4TvQBE6UIFZaKpIEXE31pyZQUU-3p5laxlVRWJVtL4qI-xGGHl7v9EHXDHLXo_FC8k/s600/DSC05092.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲遊戲設置時，玩家會輪流把手中的怪獸卡打出來，並在地圖上相對應位置放上黑色的怪獸棋子（如圖）。不管玩家打出幾張怪獸卡，只會補抽一張手牌。但若全體玩家打出的怪獸卡大於等於４張的話，將所有卡片收回重洗，重新設置～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjHU3jQuHeOwZm-P8Arukn8Qmp3GRwam5WUjuDkLmqDA3O2bfb0NoLg2miQ1QHD6e4l5g3QNdjvUqCV3FyhZYQNmUUDpw7taU-YB35KTocVzX7S1dpChEBjzgcWhi8wvohJHem3Fl7oD6h6NXutTell74S0WNbZpTWnxZGTB1ByGf9BeKqs75ufJdmzw5E/s4198/DSC05093.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjHU3jQuHeOwZm-P8Arukn8Qmp3GRwam5WUjuDkLmqDA3O2bfb0NoLg2miQ1QHD6e4l5g3QNdjvUqCV3FyhZYQNmUUDpw7taU-YB35KTocVzX7S1dpChEBjzgcWhi8wvohJHem3Fl7oD6h6NXutTell74S0WNbZpTWnxZGTB1ByGf9BeKqs75ufJdmzw5E/s600/DSC05093.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲每次輪到玩家的時候先丟骰子，上面這個是抽一張卡片的符號，其餘數字則是前進步數，還有一個符號是休息一回合～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEi8eAaqKERv7Pa-EbxxAmdHIqFlIOqAuwTXP8CmVbIldpCnNXhiaw91iizCdgHqjhcGuesSnVi_jvZzbkMgMbL93TtDrx-zju_BCZCXPCJM5TEOH0RPYhWAwjoTVI-NbfdZn88AExjsIE4KwTy8l2JUn3uuSKY5MBmPuvwuMZMMbr-EZ3X89Qeln-sX3Rs/s5262/DSC05094.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEi8eAaqKERv7Pa-EbxxAmdHIqFlIOqAuwTXP8CmVbIldpCnNXhiaw91iizCdgHqjhcGuesSnVi_jvZzbkMgMbL93TtDrx-zju_BCZCXPCJM5TEOH0RPYhWAwjoTVI-NbfdZn88AExjsIE4KwTy8l2JUn3uuSKY5MBmPuvwuMZMMbr-EZ3X89Qeln-sX3Rs/s600/DSC05094.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲踩到顏色方塊可以抽一張卡片</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEj60FhxCelqmXcgfMvnus_UltgNQ7EvmQBma7v6A4ThP_tNUT91ZGgeAommd-GsHkF2HkuRxVONLj5wdUue0ahEAYWL53XujpSigNvTyko7C5_Ds4JhoCv_bl6s5wjCtT7vQbV0WQKJycmgg7OiC9kE4bZxnuYsn6vs5Fhs7dINA-XWQlfzrmqQ06OmnQQ/s5290/DSC05095.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEj60FhxCelqmXcgfMvnus_UltgNQ7EvmQBma7v6A4ThP_tNUT91ZGgeAommd-GsHkF2HkuRxVONLj5wdUue0ahEAYWL53XujpSigNvTyko7C5_Ds4JhoCv_bl6s5wjCtT7vQbV0WQKJycmgg7OiC9kE4bZxnuYsn6vs5Fhs7dINA-XWQlfzrmqQ06OmnQQ/s600/DSC05095.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲遇到怪獸要擲骰戰鬥，擲到１的玩家打敗怪獸，並獲得立刻擲骰的好處～遇到關卡（如上圖中的湍急河流）必須從手中打出能量卡才能通過，如果能量不夠，可以找前後四格內的其他人幫忙～願意幫忙的人可以獲得１張女巫葛林達卡～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEicSdu6M0cSHbLjfcyxwI8mgHhhyphenhyphennL-onLAlZaCog170R7rEM-g3LTpF681Had8Sj7GmbV2h6pDriNr51mTW-SCD3rmpq2rlnfvx33bt4c0Q2WQlp_vz_Lmge4s3ld64BPvFGRd9CvdhUrVLtdz8mwz9Gh3nNxXwRNFji4XduiLfFSl1i56WXGR1qZCWfg/s5094/DSC05096.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEicSdu6M0cSHbLjfcyxwI8mgHhhyphenhyphennL-onLAlZaCog170R7rEM-g3LTpF681Had8Sj7GmbV2h6pDriNr51mTW-SCD3rmpq2rlnfvx33bt4c0Q2WQlp_vz_Lmge4s3ld64BPvFGRd9CvdhUrVLtdz8mwz9Gh3nNxXwRNFji4XduiLfFSl1i56WXGR1qZCWfg/s600/DSC05096.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲遊戲是半合作模式，我們必須在所有怪獸現身之前讓所有人都到達紅色城堡～否則就會一起輸掉遊戲～如果有達成過關目標，那就會比所有人手上剩餘的能量點數（女巫葛林達卡代表２點）最高的玩家獲勝！</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjgo3hcxAVfDt0jNv5vYL1B0pco0XLYSCu8X3M1MxYQHJ1sNmt9P3F6a873416vmwyQOCUYYklr6EqSpT6Hto9cZT18Y5OlFc_tuSjw7ybrEbYpITJcg0gOSzmS_F-1dIsXOghkVdaJuvTZBZ_z-KXjFAlduahQuL0dpi_yYrGRxKAuCufAOSUn06O4lfw/s4684/DSC05097.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjgo3hcxAVfDt0jNv5vYL1B0pco0XLYSCu8X3M1MxYQHJ1sNmt9P3F6a873416vmwyQOCUYYklr6EqSpT6Hto9cZT18Y5OlFc_tuSjw7ybrEbYpITJcg0gOSzmS_F-1dIsXOghkVdaJuvTZBZ_z-KXjFAlduahQuL0dpi_yYrGRxKAuCufAOSUn06O4lfw/s600/DSC05097.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲我們也來看看故事書，質感我覺得很棒～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhyqvAoIa_7141IL9zhB4YcdlnptmYE9d8XD_Vj1ifDPTP7W9IYsIonXcRNEEaMTj6qqhEJ74DBoTMlXf1wAjfrGGV0z5ILk7IrXLuH546MMxniLsnBHkHZUuzr0viHq_4Kixpt-CElOi9FCHT57KlIlMil8w-ZQ_tT2UkRLSaDW45nHdxnX__ZxHI2ZNM/s4876/DSC05098.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhyqvAoIa_7141IL9zhB4YcdlnptmYE9d8XD_Vj1ifDPTP7W9IYsIonXcRNEEaMTj6qqhEJ74DBoTMlXf1wAjfrGGV0z5ILk7IrXLuH546MMxniLsnBHkHZUuzr0viHq_4Kixpt-CElOi9FCHT57KlIlMil8w-ZQ_tT2UkRLSaDW45nHdxnX__ZxHI2ZNM/s600/DSC05098.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲插圖跟文字的搭配很舒服～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEiYbh5ZNhgL3QWxTiO9ZKf4jv95tgiXvjsaqGl30jCUqgwJyk5onnPX739IRgNXS69jmtVDTGwDWXaylhxyYz2shhCchboJrExzfnllNXFseSKo2uc14FU7HKZ3gx9uF0HoIQgkny2zOFODXOOC4lD2Wx7Fdlqg2SPdgwHqkSh97Sb61LhZFVTUuHq0aVI\"></p><p><strong>老實說遊戲有點太兒童～</strong></p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">這款遊戲如果要用一般『桌遊人』的眼光來看～不是那麼的桌遊～就像我前面說的，也有可能是我一開始對它的期望拉太高～所以難免會有一點的小失望～但我相信這款遊戲的受眾不是所謂的『桌遊人』～更何況『桌遊人』的標準有多機車大家應該也都明白～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">但缺點反過來看也正是它的優點～由於遊戲規則不難～所以這款遊戲我會推薦給想要介紹《綠野仙蹤》這個故事給小朋友們認識的家長或是老師們～如果是帶著孩子們共讀，然後接著一起玩這款遊戲，那就會相當的不錯～甚至我會覺得建議年齡１０＋有點拉太高～其實聽得懂故事的孩子就可以抓來玩這款遊戲了～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">雖然遊戲的部分我算是小失望～但故事書我會給很高的評價～很漂亮的插畫版面跟紙質～文字的排版閱讀起來也相當的舒服～讓我有機會可以重新惡補這個我自以為已經很熟悉的《綠野仙蹤》，讀完之後才知道我對這個故事其實還有好多的無知～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p>最後附上購買資訊：</p><p>綠野仙蹤（書）、（書＋桌遊）組合:</p><p>博客來：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/4ePmzBZ\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/4ePmzBZ</a></p><p>誠品：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/45PGtJ0\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/45PGtJ0</a></p><p>官網：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3W7Kl4V\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3W7Kl4V</a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiTU2zAYeywmDC-ptyS092nf2XE80MtrDfPMomDrdhAY-lty_l_yHpzxFHlvlZDkPmZDlyIIs2_E9Zd94H9f2alvj5sLXEHMn76pzGg6KKSIv0c80udsDnWpMjt0BkQXgKf9e6oXTZfOBuD4_l-_h8AO1UXh6L6zds-xmSYh2Q5A3Pm5VkMtzw3me7t64Y/s5472/DSC05099.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiTU2zAYeywmDC-ptyS092nf2XE80MtrDfPMomDrdhAY-lty_l_yHpzxFHlvlZDkPmZDlyIIs2_E9Zd94H9f2alvj5sLXEHMn76pzGg6KKSIv0c80udsDnWpMjt0BkQXgKf9e6oXTZfOBuD4_l-_h8AO1UXh6L6zds-xmSYh2Q5A3Pm5VkMtzw3me7t64Y/s600/DSC05099.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p><br></p>', '2024-11-18 09:46:33', '2024-11-18 09:46:33', 1, 'forum-1731894392973-298598734.jpg'),
(13, 1, '【桌遊開箱報】Sea Salt & Paper 海鹽摺紙 開箱＋介紹', '<h3><br></h3><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEi10ku2-t4FdpXza5kbM_sHL4WdN4-HbO8F2LJeHPM7lxufBvlCNFHt0NCPkmZKVdxiibCD3en33nnrC2QkoK-tp9uSPGZkXxoG3AkTKyU1jN1O55mEdGHSOYI-IESPhPfcuWLRoh08k0MArdNoQaSBjC3abfLEsZAmApJPhP4f5onwStsTxZKZS2NdZV4/s2880/DSC05054.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEi10ku2-t4FdpXza5kbM_sHL4WdN4-HbO8F2LJeHPM7lxufBvlCNFHt0NCPkmZKVdxiibCD3en33nnrC2QkoK-tp9uSPGZkXxoG3AkTKyU1jN1O55mEdGHSOYI-IESPhPfcuWLRoh08k0MArdNoQaSBjC3abfLEsZAmApJPhP4f5onwStsTxZKZS2NdZV4/s600/DSC05054.JPG\"></a></p><p><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEg2NcXP29U0fW7PzRgW4wGt4cUXRnO4HKctvYohRgnYeyzKqPzSOTiipYD960P4qV8yDjdo9HXA_Bi0Tf5dx8netM1wU_2BFeaCwVLwrL5YnVjbxI00uSJ1eHEmq1Vnffls94N-NIFuGofQDvs1boYimMEkpTAFSTapY0ugCGn07wHZUWylEnlMOv1q9QQ\"></p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">《Sea Salt &amp; Paper 海鹽摺紙》一開始我沒get到它的名稱梗，還以為這個標題是隨便組出來的，後來才發現原來是rock paper scissors（剪刀石頭布）裡面的paper跟scissors的諧音梗～《Sea Salt &amp; Paper 海鹽摺紙》是一款美術風格相當獨特且漂亮的遊戲，遊戲規則輕快好教，但同時又保有其獨特之處～一起來看看這款遊戲吧～</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEj-XYIv3kJn33d5J8DcqO7t5ugh1CgZvfoFqenPf-7dkWiNDG8k8z9s5O7g7YbfLHt67nVFSz7T2QUkwBO2BKM420AUnajlaxAl1DPPx1y3CZs0THGPLKXmB6PtX2UHZdWy2ZlV6qZEPfAKhJWKFf7hl3C-T81_nZhOJTcHIjyQq1jhgVp_l494SayY178\"></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEi10ku2-t4FdpXza5kbM_sHL4WdN4-HbO8F2LJeHPM7lxufBvlCNFHt0NCPkmZKVdxiibCD3en33nnrC2QkoK-tp9uSPGZkXxoG3AkTKyU1jN1O55mEdGHSOYI-IESPhPfcuWLRoh08k0MArdNoQaSBjC3abfLEsZAmApJPhP4f5onwStsTxZKZS2NdZV4/s2880/DSC05054.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEi10ku2-t4FdpXza5kbM_sHL4WdN4-HbO8F2LJeHPM7lxufBvlCNFHt0NCPkmZKVdxiibCD3en33nnrC2QkoK-tp9uSPGZkXxoG3AkTKyU1jN1O55mEdGHSOYI-IESPhPfcuWLRoh08k0MArdNoQaSBjC3abfLEsZAmApJPhP4f5onwStsTxZKZS2NdZV4/s600/DSC05054.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲封面不得不說真的很特別，也很美～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjVRLTem7h0yjURzKrxHy-2VC_K9ULcgHSvVM7z89UjD9BWbg_7iigNA1poLBTE_8gZbhDoqRH35K3hG328_WrQKEc5jEGLBKWD3fuJlypDWdLnsPSoPsk4SG7JNhvdHV3HJEA2N_bpI3qOOt5GdAccFW3WcGjTEVBLqZcGP0eUZA66UOESplKP9U_OXKU/s4320/DSC05055.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjVRLTem7h0yjURzKrxHy-2VC_K9ULcgHSvVM7z89UjD9BWbg_7iigNA1poLBTE_8gZbhDoqRH35K3hG328_WrQKEc5jEGLBKWD3fuJlypDWdLnsPSoPsk4SG7JNhvdHV3HJEA2N_bpI3qOOt5GdAccFW3WcGjTEVBLqZcGP0eUZA66UOESplKP9U_OXKU/s600/DSC05055.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲遊戲人數：2-4人　建議年齡：8+　遊戲時間：30 mins</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEi5f9YeUBlXiwCo0S0za8P45xkdb7L1zhin0_V01YstVZdGHqRyX6n-j7X_nGM-AVZM1p2cio0BWyP_B1U0jgVvqV9kphcFB4UBZ-cjFTxll14PpVJs0dLBFPElYV-Y_n3s8rlq3FkgEaVBhf6J13qnx6NJ50-xzjHcy7TtSH_kM1hsAUdd4X-ImFPQskM/s2400/DSC05056.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEi5f9YeUBlXiwCo0S0za8P45xkdb7L1zhin0_V01YstVZdGHqRyX6n-j7X_nGM-AVZM1p2cio0BWyP_B1U0jgVvqV9kphcFB4UBZ-cjFTxll14PpVJs0dLBFPElYV-Y_n3s8rlq3FkgEaVBhf6J13qnx6NJ50-xzjHcy7TtSH_kM1hsAUdd4X-ImFPQskM/s600/DSC05056.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲背面有更多的卡片，可能是板面太小，所以沒有遊戲遊玩照片</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh-zMrdd6Ew5b_Gu3xgMCTeHfFVRWPskx602TScNJBAPYWxmlkLFUPXPdJN3-4pV535DbIvmCXH7sk-Z2jEslefJDAXNJW0nLfY6HU_j_Abrh-d0Y_pW5dJcSvho2SBsYXma66BEBlrKJzw8BDckIn2dhmDLCOojjiwRPayXiWwOS48cch-jFIcu7abhfs/s3752/DSC05057.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh-zMrdd6Ew5b_Gu3xgMCTeHfFVRWPskx602TScNJBAPYWxmlkLFUPXPdJN3-4pV535DbIvmCXH7sk-Z2jEslefJDAXNJW0nLfY6HU_j_Abrh-d0Y_pW5dJcSvho2SBsYXma66BEBlrKJzw8BDckIn2dhmDLCOojjiwRPayXiWwOS48cch-jFIcu7abhfs/s600/DSC05057.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲內容物一覽</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhY5Eb-9lZjoj7JAnHeqFVAHTxKr3UyIDup4gM3crq3oR74Fi6LI2x5KGu9oqPJFqGrxcTVJqtgoXLdH8hAfNXL2rebsN8h_BTVpU8WRX6oW-tfeGEx4zXAvU0xRd2REOzUDOQh03e4vJNFPEpYBgMlcCOKNHjmPvWip9OFVN213hWx7w4fVvMZk_cORsI/s3924/DSC05058.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhY5Eb-9lZjoj7JAnHeqFVAHTxKr3UyIDup4gM3crq3oR74Fi6LI2x5KGu9oqPJFqGrxcTVJqtgoXLdH8hAfNXL2rebsN8h_BTVpU8WRX6oW-tfeGEx4zXAvU0xRd2REOzUDOQh03e4vJNFPEpYBgMlcCOKNHjmPvWip9OFVN213hWx7w4fVvMZk_cORsI/s600/DSC05058.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲主要就是卡片一包</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiDhrcNLkuHr5eVZ09-gZNFbAf14e3hAJoZIXTFGFXoVrUS9m_oxnRpEoUChFWF0r4kCEqA2nZKT4NRaC7NPkAXQmjKXL25QIaJ7vXFUTBAxSfZKN5pBLTRToADJpdmGGRqGLn6FODMOumkdR2w6wCvhqA_CN8347INMd42XmmtvDhqWQEhBuPWXxQcejI/s4348/DSC05059.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiDhrcNLkuHr5eVZ09-gZNFbAf14e3hAJoZIXTFGFXoVrUS9m_oxnRpEoUChFWF0r4kCEqA2nZKT4NRaC7NPkAXQmjKXL25QIaJ7vXFUTBAxSfZKN5pBLTRToADJpdmGGRqGLn6FODMOumkdR2w6wCvhqA_CN8347INMd42XmmtvDhqWQEhBuPWXxQcejI/s600/DSC05059.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲卡片內容有：手牌一疊、玩家幫助卡一張、顏色幫助卡一張</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgikkt5XiPfmuK-8nTOY6QjQkgH6YV2UDR0VfJ-Cwk09H_qsh1ANZmpffPQ8n85bwMlOosZDQRzi7EaMOPKkCAqqKsIr6a8DuR_uSjUUnqiELXGd4baq41DwNVTlIE4OvOB2k9y0WXpEBQxL3S1J4JD8zIBWWp6Igs6d6yE3dwbbZuqBy5Ou6SrdI5qwFc/s3528/DSC05060.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgikkt5XiPfmuK-8nTOY6QjQkgH6YV2UDR0VfJ-Cwk09H_qsh1ANZmpffPQ8n85bwMlOosZDQRzi7EaMOPKkCAqqKsIr6a8DuR_uSjUUnqiELXGd4baq41DwNVTlIE4OvOB2k9y0WXpEBQxL3S1J4JD8zIBWWp6Igs6d6yE3dwbbZuqBy5Ou6SrdI5qwFc/s600/DSC05060.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲來照一張所有的卡片，摺紙真的很可愛～</p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEj154z3TFbOF0IIVnFn3AkdJkpQVyATxRxw38jAO8ckBMLGiNMowwDU5Yiyaphw-dRFZKKpTmpI2-wjFzabhCX-skC6wy8fKX61boNbbgsQwDKsLZtBfIZ-48F0V-zBq1aPwpNIabHiv486eDD5z9jAk-8uNgBISzcPKpPv8gp_uchKW6j2GO8T97R3ihY/s4152/DSC05063.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEj154z3TFbOF0IIVnFn3AkdJkpQVyATxRxw38jAO8ckBMLGiNMowwDU5Yiyaphw-dRFZKKpTmpI2-wjFzabhCX-skC6wy8fKX61boNbbgsQwDKsLZtBfIZ-48F0V-zBq1aPwpNIabHiv486eDD5z9jAk-8uNgBISzcPKpPv8gp_uchKW6j2GO8T97R3ihY/s600/DSC05063.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲隨意抓幾張讓大家看得更清楚些～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhU_4ZcpiRHbdfxuyQmQUIMH5ka_2rTLWrJ1n0h6-Sb78E8aSNaUuuSw5-uiw5qSiDiahkn9m47f6XGJJjAuRUqrAz3urTf9RCkUflaXqO1mHmcSwpDWcIg2HjslKAoWYm__UKi78bkhLANBGVyl-2ePiXPgCGfSJ-hWQofySa1rdU6XjJ_Mg_Jrl96bSE/s2740/DSC05064.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhU_4ZcpiRHbdfxuyQmQUIMH5ka_2rTLWrJ1n0h6-Sb78E8aSNaUuuSw5-uiw5qSiDiahkn9m47f6XGJJjAuRUqrAz3urTf9RCkUflaXqO1mHmcSwpDWcIg2HjslKAoWYm__UKi78bkhLANBGVyl-2ePiXPgCGfSJ-hWQofySa1rdU6XjJ_Mg_Jrl96bSE/s600/DSC05064.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲玩家幫助卡</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhYMgcWQFmlYWZPg-nl073wE7a-woH-zc82Ut9C0LZxB0VVTJPJmPBdyd2wyQqb4mM9-JZ68GPdhZNoErO5T_nTdvZrYy3LsaEANFUqrhzDsyKa5oe7_H0Pm4MLyD95A2SzZFyGS9Kixg0JMH0kGG2TsRBG8bqQ2NTNqT4PvAPubXxTyxxtzE5FtOEO4wk/s4364/DSC05068.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhYMgcWQFmlYWZPg-nl073wE7a-woH-zc82Ut9C0LZxB0VVTJPJmPBdyd2wyQqb4mM9-JZ68GPdhZNoErO5T_nTdvZrYy3LsaEANFUqrhzDsyKa5oe7_H0Pm4MLyD95A2SzZFyGS9Kixg0JMH0kGG2TsRBG8bqQ2NTNqT4PvAPubXxTyxxtzE5FtOEO4wk/s600/DSC05068.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲遊戲內盒的圖樣也很漂亮</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEhJ4_aghNvyQ-cdKmQXMeIbqrgRWpwmFaJWAM7xl7LNbEHZoOt5JQYNdlfIh-Y2vclQZBX7Y25AvxeBbVWYl_-BoF0zLB38lzv8vfVkvDfBRMneESc6tVV1bwb5fL-gaZ18cy0__pcbJ-RXr3qz_sm4c29-YB9OJ6NFyZWtaWqACgpjeo941T69j9s9fCA\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgGCTTEa_ZyscQYAbaOfwXx7FnsoPNjxJlLP1AlTbccU7XmV0JbvCwLiJ_VU8og3f-6nagJdOqfwlfxjrkRQh1f7-kHMwTJ5jyZHHlgIV-TMRglLgQwcxsmW-ky3MPwH-mWt9d70E2yd6h6oWqkzwup2QWlHFcNOqzlemPHZZtF4f0zkDiw0bSyAg1Jxpg/s4852/DSC05065.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgGCTTEa_ZyscQYAbaOfwXx7FnsoPNjxJlLP1AlTbccU7XmV0JbvCwLiJ_VU8og3f-6nagJdOqfwlfxjrkRQh1f7-kHMwTJ5jyZHHlgIV-TMRglLgQwcxsmW-ky3MPwH-mWt9d70E2yd6h6oWqkzwup2QWlHFcNOqzlemPHZZtF4f0zkDiw0bSyAg1Jxpg/s600/DSC05065.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲將所有卡片洗牌，然後隨機翻開兩張成為兩疊棄牌堆，隨機選一個人當起始玩家，這樣遊戲就設置完成了！有沒有很簡單！</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEie4Ylglz6O5D_ZLmI2qWxhcBQBph4kDxmK6ZyPDFRn5JQuEavqerAY4SQe8WH41_XCqfJ5M3S3MJGafL8BDvfCOocCVCa6p3pBKL3KwnntwDAtx_Ab1lVZTcVwiUfiRSXKfW4G6W_n1fL4Dt8XmoTlyY3piwUoFaIEljphT90otwvvnBP93AjjiJpL-Vo/s4796/DSC05066.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEie4Ylglz6O5D_ZLmI2qWxhcBQBph4kDxmK6ZyPDFRn5JQuEavqerAY4SQe8WH41_XCqfJ5M3S3MJGafL8BDvfCOocCVCa6p3pBKL3KwnntwDAtx_Ab1lVZTcVwiUfiRSXKfW4G6W_n1fL4Dt8XmoTlyY3piwUoFaIEljphT90otwvvnBP93AjjiJpL-Vo/s600/DSC05066.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲每次輪到你的時候，可以選擇：</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">１．從牌庫抽二留一</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">２．拿走其中一個棄牌堆最上面那張卡</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">接著你可以選擇打出成對卡片或是結束～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiozZiYq899wytuqVeo18jGV4jRg0a8d-iB36S_qM7dhXbMBKzFRuBInzTpKQcZpwzMRsE2zwunIDcVnmhfI_8K8F0zLwTRy2e020t8bWplwAt12oYkqxxIl0ut1x6A_9pHqCCS8ckF4zOoPwH0A7EJRKpKSzQ0eJgIH2skXS8O-wxXzsFvMDp_P6zuKpI/s3740/DSC05067.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiozZiYq899wytuqVeo18jGV4jRg0a8d-iB36S_qM7dhXbMBKzFRuBInzTpKQcZpwzMRsE2zwunIDcVnmhfI_8K8F0zLwTRy2e020t8bWplwAt12oYkqxxIl0ut1x6A_9pHqCCS8ckF4zOoPwH0A7EJRKpKSzQ0eJgIH2skXS8O-wxXzsFvMDp_P6zuKpI/s600/DSC05067.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲成對的卡片有四種，如果你手上有不只一組成對卡片，你可以一直打一直打～卡片的左上角都有簡易圖示來告訴你誰跟誰是成對的，很好懂。每組打出來的成對卡片都價值一分，接著來說說他們的功能：</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">１．兩隻魚：從牌庫頂端抽一張卡片，加入你的手牌</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">２．兩艘船：立刻再進行一個回合</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">３．兩隻蟹：拿走其中一疊棄牌堆，從中選走一張牌之後放回整疊棄牌堆（不改變順序）</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">４．一人＋一鯊：選擇一位玩家，隨機抽走他一張手牌</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">美人魚是比較特殊的卡片，每輪結束的時候，會根據你擁有的最多顏色卡片讓你獲得分數。如果你有兩隻美人魚，那你擁有的前兩多顏色的卡片每張都會給你一分...依此類推～但如果你同時擁有四隻美人魚！你贏了！遊戲直接結束！</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">其他卡片都是成套蒐集，我就不特別說明了，很簡單的～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhU_4ZcpiRHbdfxuyQmQUIMH5ka_2rTLWrJ1n0h6-Sb78E8aSNaUuuSw5-uiw5qSiDiahkn9m47f6XGJJjAuRUqrAz3urTf9RCkUflaXqO1mHmcSwpDWcIg2HjslKAoWYm__UKi78bkhLANBGVyl-2ePiXPgCGfSJ-hWQofySa1rdU6XjJ_Mg_Jrl96bSE/s600/DSC05064.JPG\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲隨著遊戲的進行，玩家們會有打出成對卡片的分數（每一對一分），還會有手牌中成套收集的分數，當你的分數有七分以上時，就可以在回合結束之後決定結束這輪～（當然也可以不作聲繼續玩）如果你決定結束這輪，你有兩種選擇：</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">１．宣布【到此為止】：所有玩家立刻結束動作，並各自結算自己的分數。</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">２．宣布【最後機會】：除了你之外，所有玩家再進行一次動作接著算分</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">－如果你還是最高分（並列也算）</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">你除了得到卡牌總分還能加上顏色獎勵</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">其他玩家只能獲得顏色獎勵</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">－如果你不是最高分</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">你只能獲得顏色獎勵</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">其他玩家獲得卡牌總分</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">＊顏色獎勵＝擁有的最多顏色的卡片數量（每張一分）</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">遊戲為總分制，２／３／４人遊戲，結束分數為４０／３５／３０分</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">若還沒有人達到結束分數，由剛剛結束那輪玩家的左手邊玩家開始下一輪～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEiYbh5ZNhgL3QWxTiO9ZKf4jv95tgiXvjsaqGl30jCUqgwJyk5onnPX739IRgNXS69jmtVDTGwDWXaylhxyYz2shhCchboJrExzfnllNXFseSKo2uc14FU7HKZ3gx9uF0HoIQgkny2zOFODXOOC4lD2Wx7Fdlqg2SPdgwHqkSh97Sb61LhZFVTUuHq0aVI\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>可愛且獨特</strong></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">在還沒玩過《Sea Salt &amp; Paper 海鹽摺紙》之前，我以為它就是一款美術獨特的可愛遊戲～但真正玩過才知道，原來它連規則都很獨特～除了讓玩家們決定何時喊停來結算之外，還要決定是直接結算或是讓其他人再動作一次～這種帶有一點『賭』又需要有一些判斷力的決策其實相當的有趣～也是讓整款遊戲變得擁有很獨特的魅力所在！</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">美術用摺紙來呈現真的是非常的舒服，尤其是當今ＡＩ越來越會畫圖的當下，這種看到實體照片呈現出的美感更是可以讓人感受到更多的溫度～（會不會改天ＡＩ連這種風格都能畫了？）這款遊戲我會推薦給：喜歡海洋生物的玩家、喜歡摺紙風格的玩家、想要找一款快速家庭遊戲的玩家、還有每個擁有赤子之心的你！</p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhJrcJHS3NVMh1Lfd64skAGAUnh21p34_nvW_QO31gCsSmPa1oml6mxx_uGHke1xEqv2A_j8BJqCew-AFVnCO6eYLPWaZ5HHe0xCglfkXYY-FCSSQJIjuNrN5I8ghhxQGGMnRZpkJS_WA4pJymN47LUPSDR2MlMA8h0aWKX3-oy78g6WHZOjMSI5g_Z_Ko/s4528/DSC05069.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhJrcJHS3NVMh1Lfd64skAGAUnh21p34_nvW_QO31gCsSmPa1oml6mxx_uGHke1xEqv2A_j8BJqCew-AFVnCO6eYLPWaZ5HHe0xCglfkXYY-FCSSQJIjuNrN5I8ghhxQGGMnRZpkJS_WA4pJymN47LUPSDR2MlMA8h0aWKX3-oy78g6WHZOjMSI5g_Z_Ko/s600/DSC05069.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲遊戲收納照</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEimuwMSBfA8tyrUUI7MjRyoxwM6_RnoZj62iE4V6kHxOq1i1gYSZ5JzBco_H-Ou9-ttdAW7LI1V8Cw378d34plpW79dZy-XH2wpsU2PuM1RZJfWsdKjaMBmnr_COxt6dmfsiguRkJqOtgfmWHWZY4zlboLu-lf_0OiDvNwRGTzp9UzgmxdQY5VzQBJ7Lw8/s5138/DSC05062.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEimuwMSBfA8tyrUUI7MjRyoxwM6_RnoZj62iE4V6kHxOq1i1gYSZ5JzBco_H-Ou9-ttdAW7LI1V8Cw378d34plpW79dZy-XH2wpsU2PuM1RZJfWsdKjaMBmnr_COxt6dmfsiguRkJqOtgfmWHWZY4zlboLu-lf_0OiDvNwRGTzp9UzgmxdQY5VzQBJ7Lw8/s600/DSC05062.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgT9mgAUqG9iT1EEUqmvn49RDq1OPsLKOtxJVpP48nvTgL9Tjci3gW3oVAHjsyINEtOsk3GW_QN4wCBtc9EOkZ-tEt5Ja9Z7y_VF3GbIdOJScUxCvml8vAmR_GhyphenhyphenLLRnS8d7BHFLZ8Kslt7Huy38bxOtXj_xu-EslybsKlmi_HpI9FZs1U1_WAUKMQzX6U/s5472/DSC05061.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgT9mgAUqG9iT1EEUqmvn49RDq1OPsLKOtxJVpP48nvTgL9Tjci3gW3oVAHjsyINEtOsk3GW_QN4wCBtc9EOkZ-tEt5Ja9Z7y_VF3GbIdOJScUxCvml8vAmR_GhyphenhyphenLLRnS8d7BHFLZ8Kslt7Huy38bxOtXj_xu-EslybsKlmi_HpI9FZs1U1_WAUKMQzX6U/s600/DSC05061.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p><br></p>', '2024-11-18 10:20:14', '2024-11-18 10:20:14', 1, 'forum-1731896414201-341962767.jpg');
INSERT INTO `forum_posts` (`id`, `user_id`, `title`, `content`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `status`, `cover_image`) VALUES
(14, 1, '【桌遊開箱報】Saboteur 矮人礦坑 二十週年紀念版 開箱+介紹', '<h3><br></h3><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh_C4g06o8N8aosnJj6psBLobUiC0Rw2WTVnhuYuisqsXQWYnDztakFzyl-owr2je6JrhY_nmkxRSTV-VpINdDAoxoALznFI_AQHTfG1ZmnX8SReuDPaQRQo941PFjXw4bZup1fAqnkL7KxEYutLyJ7ZMKv2XX5HyTaV9pb_BfBJGd4FYviWQoB_6OQIjs/s3192/DSC05010.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh_C4g06o8N8aosnJj6psBLobUiC0Rw2WTVnhuYuisqsXQWYnDztakFzyl-owr2je6JrhY_nmkxRSTV-VpINdDAoxoALznFI_AQHTfG1ZmnX8SReuDPaQRQo941PFjXw4bZup1fAqnkL7KxEYutLyJ7ZMKv2XX5HyTaV9pb_BfBJGd4FYviWQoB_6OQIjs/s600/DSC05010.JPG\"></a></p><p><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEiM8fOGisB5RG54sdUxUDAacMJZqU39sLOG9tfkLGwb2oAnyQK5UOEbDn_gKkxvThijN9WgOwtLQ_z93c9FjZbk785a1_8I_GlUMXnZVyP1YCmnkdhyXeGdk5GV9r5uitSBu2rae3AM9OC0IfpZ0tr8_78liV8qqhyKf4weB9yDOZlNxd4jPdJyq2I3RrY\"></p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">《Saboteur 矮人礦坑》是一款十年前的經典遊戲！（＊＆＊＃＆＊！＃＆＊！＠＆＃以上省略一百句髒話）咳！《Saboteur 矮人礦坑》居然已經二十週年啦！想當初我都還沒出生，一轉眼我都已經十八歲了呢！（被拖出去打死）總之，這款遊戲沒什麼好說的，就是我桌遊的啟蒙、就是我桌遊的起點、就是我呆呆地站在鏡子前、就是我桌墊下的老照片、就是記憶中妳青澀的臉（夠了，可以了），這次的二十週年紀念版，我還不寫爆！</p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEj-XYIv3kJn33d5J8DcqO7t5ugh1CgZvfoFqenPf-7dkWiNDG8k8z9s5O7g7YbfLHt67nVFSz7T2QUkwBO2BKM420AUnajlaxAl1DPPx1y3CZs0THGPLKXmB6PtX2UHZdWy2ZlV6qZEPfAKhJWKFf7hl3C-T81_nZhOJTcHIjyQq1jhgVp_l494SayY178\"></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh_C4g06o8N8aosnJj6psBLobUiC0Rw2WTVnhuYuisqsXQWYnDztakFzyl-owr2je6JrhY_nmkxRSTV-VpINdDAoxoALznFI_AQHTfG1ZmnX8SReuDPaQRQo941PFjXw4bZup1fAqnkL7KxEYutLyJ7ZMKv2XX5HyTaV9pb_BfBJGd4FYviWQoB_6OQIjs/s3192/DSC05010.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh_C4g06o8N8aosnJj6psBLobUiC0Rw2WTVnhuYuisqsXQWYnDztakFzyl-owr2je6JrhY_nmkxRSTV-VpINdDAoxoALznFI_AQHTfG1ZmnX8SReuDPaQRQo941PFjXw4bZup1fAqnkL7KxEYutLyJ7ZMKv2XX5HyTaV9pb_BfBJGd4FYviWQoB_6OQIjs/s600/DSC05010.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲封面整個變得比較優雅～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh48ZdeUNb7CHZg9nfeUrx19NQyC_zx31iGb-4BKStozgUQdt9v8saBIv10y8yEML1Xb2h013kwNYuIILbz_26o2N9gyH1hUc_B2XND1Lsb4DGSvTl_7XllW5DLcnqg4jJuAY3LJwa4Fv8jhECGGbiY0nUaZcjQ8StvhFvysqKvxj0jk_GrpAG3BadLszQ/s3688/DSC05011.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh48ZdeUNb7CHZg9nfeUrx19NQyC_zx31iGb-4BKStozgUQdt9v8saBIv10y8yEML1Xb2h013kwNYuIILbz_26o2N9gyH1hUc_B2XND1Lsb4DGSvTl_7XllW5DLcnqg4jJuAY3LJwa4Fv8jhECGGbiY0nUaZcjQ8StvhFvysqKvxj0jk_GrpAG3BadLszQ/s600/DSC05011.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲遊戲人數：2-12人　建議年齡：8+　遊戲時間：30 mins</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">經過這麼多年，還是很難找到在遊玩人數上超越矮人礦坑的遊戲！</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEi_wAjXSpmHE8VqcUCWPMRFHJaJEU3umrAGw6BMSNf3WWUTy_uwFGY-6po1EUbMWKvF52J87yrQUTbcEuRaYHkXsW6VWfo0SJbQoELxnWaDeN8aurIuYWglTdxjlvi27dB1xBtEgXBLGt2eEr0zGmVi3omECf3H_3UygBzeeD2AEe-O0XZZ2UBmpeogyro/s3072/DSC05012.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEi_wAjXSpmHE8VqcUCWPMRFHJaJEU3umrAGw6BMSNf3WWUTy_uwFGY-6po1EUbMWKvF52J87yrQUTbcEuRaYHkXsW6VWfo0SJbQoELxnWaDeN8aurIuYWglTdxjlvi27dB1xBtEgXBLGt2eEr0zGmVi3omECf3H_3UygBzeeD2AEe-O0XZZ2UBmpeogyro/s600/DSC05012.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲背面沒有圖片，只有文字</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgl79QfGPzhLtYRIWyFg_3GCmDr0byT8FIb5XAlfo7qysckE7h6iPt1fh2a1VIVjH9daPalM9hJ_WXuNwTRzlrpAMpoyO4WwwsY5YPiKGAth8hv6k4V8Jjyb1S4Wt3snvBi4fNeBc8UST_a-iNeBbrmNliWSaqrS2QK2TnOW7PQA1Q5SUc1-vnCCVcxlF4/s3132/DSC05013.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgl79QfGPzhLtYRIWyFg_3GCmDr0byT8FIb5XAlfo7qysckE7h6iPt1fh2a1VIVjH9daPalM9hJ_WXuNwTRzlrpAMpoyO4WwwsY5YPiKGAth8hv6k4V8Jjyb1S4Wt3snvBi4fNeBc8UST_a-iNeBbrmNliWSaqrS2QK2TnOW7PQA1Q5SUc1-vnCCVcxlF4/s600/DSC05013.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲但還是有一張中文的夾頁在背面</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">可以看到內容物超級豐富！</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhgK3dy5h5Hu1hTzTFE7Zf5Sga5IfGCNzGk5UHtI7fmXee1KtyPuPsrn5EZv1RCKanXKhXwz371CcVBcUliyJ1GLXXNd4zHnfuamWt0hBgDkjjGjpJBtXTF0J3e6y4DNfKhDGkKpTfz60qIKxgEtaBjYtvgtFGx2s4kkdJ-afQQFVfb-LTz3HFXhfJ2vHo/s4540/DSC05014.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhgK3dy5h5Hu1hTzTFE7Zf5Sga5IfGCNzGk5UHtI7fmXee1KtyPuPsrn5EZv1RCKanXKhXwz371CcVBcUliyJ1GLXXNd4zHnfuamWt0hBgDkjjGjpJBtXTF0J3e6y4DNfKhDGkKpTfz60qIKxgEtaBjYtvgtFGx2s4kkdJ-afQQFVfb-LTz3HFXhfJ2vHo/s600/DSC05014.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲內容物一覽</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh71KcRCYkGrKXAUnXqUgB79127d2LJiH-nF-FUDeSWyyrxsBOgnINGhZqCMgWlgdCMPFD5qM9VwiywaOizpUJ2553P8HuqAknCq5l_Wu9OrNBNatXo3rxhKTTR70zZ028ilt5MmwZFhzGXyjDOBxmHt2dQn0pgLkxrtqe8onTl9jZ4EHeVZIkoTd5nhR8/s3572/DSC05015.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh71KcRCYkGrKXAUnXqUgB79127d2LJiH-nF-FUDeSWyyrxsBOgnINGhZqCMgWlgdCMPFD5qM9VwiywaOizpUJ2553P8HuqAknCq5l_Wu9OrNBNatXo3rxhKTTR70zZ028ilt5MmwZFhzGXyjDOBxmHt2dQn0pgLkxrtqe8onTl9jZ4EHeVZIkoTd5nhR8/s600/DSC05015.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲盒子是用這樣的方式開啟</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEi5p_l991R7V8y7PVqe3-dk8wRbAJT5gQ7wlhT4CXYdBfj5vm6O7Uphyphenhyphen8hqGUVn07BdbjKVyMjU4y-H1DOaIUsU14nPqcFVbXwt7ls2-JeMOhnI_WRG2uSGFPPzY16-PkagCIRcPbk2E-raIRQ_Jj_WBZ0m03TQpmy2t6n_sYYO9YhqotN-2TKkY1fYJ58/s3932/DSC05016.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEi5p_l991R7V8y7PVqe3-dk8wRbAJT5gQ7wlhT4CXYdBfj5vm6O7Uphyphenhyphen8hqGUVn07BdbjKVyMjU4y-H1DOaIUsU14nPqcFVbXwt7ls2-JeMOhnI_WRG2uSGFPPzY16-PkagCIRcPbk2E-raIRQ_Jj_WBZ0m03TQpmy2t6n_sYYO9YhqotN-2TKkY1fYJ58/s600/DSC05016.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲說明書內可以看到所有的卡片內容</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgSZT3Ua_CT52SZli-RscFYdPTg2gFixKZdqhfzfhRUhvgdTh3y2ADYUE7Gq9zRbMUDIGhmFnYogFOi-oV93dE6SLjCxZotvkAmCoCt-YIAu0lDamSogZZrdOxwdjpOeTb3fz1uup_p_vG9IKDh7LmydMOUFIX3VaWS1-Ho_XqYSQfPIPsd6PeULu24VLM/s5204/DSC05017.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgSZT3Ua_CT52SZli-RscFYdPTg2gFixKZdqhfzfhRUhvgdTh3y2ADYUE7Gq9zRbMUDIGhmFnYogFOi-oV93dE6SLjCxZotvkAmCoCt-YIAu0lDamSogZZrdOxwdjpOeTb3fz1uup_p_vG9IKDh7LmydMOUFIX3VaWS1-Ho_XqYSQfPIPsd6PeULu24VLM/s600/DSC05017.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲戳戳樂一小張</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjLxLF1343jq0awnGk049uRN8SjbDKdqMyvWIk2-4RqpXQtRlYi3GbhrAPBy4BW9sn8O_N3Jfc7APAMRdFbzt1VJOdHCqt1HlBVmjQtksPvH5A50oHuN0RCLThk_BiG2UnluNAp5EGE-t88-vV0Eo-VDBJUTE4j_Y4Tg-wJ-HDfKhK9Nb5ZUq9vw2tpncw/s5180/DSC05018.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjLxLF1343jq0awnGk049uRN8SjbDKdqMyvWIk2-4RqpXQtRlYi3GbhrAPBy4BW9sn8O_N3Jfc7APAMRdFbzt1VJOdHCqt1HlBVmjQtksPvH5A50oHuN0RCLThk_BiG2UnluNAp5EGE-t88-vV0Eo-VDBJUTE4j_Y4Tg-wJ-HDfKhK9Nb5ZUq9vw2tpncw/s600/DSC05018.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲戳出來之後的指示物本身就是一個小擴充《矮人收費員》：遊戲設置時，每位玩家拿一片金塊六角片。玩家在回合中新增一個行動選項：棄掉任何一張手牌讓矮人收費員進場。玩家在棄掉卡片之後不能抽牌，因此之後手牌會少一張，將一個矮人收費員放在某個開放路徑的尾端，並拿取一個對應的小指示物放在自己面前。之後有任何玩家想要從該路徑連接出新的路線，就必須支付一片金塊六角片給放置矮人的玩家（也可以叫其他玩家幫你付）。每位矮人每回合最多只能進場一次。</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgVe0XrvHZvAcc1SysTrtzxb7PjVDHrkl3Jn6gjWc6reLzQ3lxUuaeMNQidzY9iiVYPPwZT-FmEt9cDnqyV_O0RoQnf-B5PXkjo51UdxJCvsQeU-zlWCHtlM2ApiwJnoXe-GgGjEj_KvKhwvr2Y8ki5j7XLTnXedE1DAfRQZzWGtv1zy_5u5u8KBziEIy0/s3302/DSC05019.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgVe0XrvHZvAcc1SysTrtzxb7PjVDHrkl3Jn6gjWc6reLzQ3lxUuaeMNQidzY9iiVYPPwZT-FmEt9cDnqyV_O0RoQnf-B5PXkjo51UdxJCvsQeU-zlWCHtlM2ApiwJnoXe-GgGjEj_KvKhwvr2Y8ki5j7XLTnXedE1DAfRQZzWGtv1zy_5u5u8KBziEIy0/s600/DSC05019.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲【坑道派對擴充】這是一張雙面明信片的其中一面</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">當有人連接到坑道派對時，洗混所有人的矮人卡，在不檢視的情況下，隨機發回給所有玩家一人一張～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiIXX9csavauQWsLdR0qrVZZEQ2RpXqk_m17ShQSpKYOoL_G7m_9clcIpNbCFd3hsnAQ83SmlllCTVf8qnnu25Uds1GTnGXmPLdnRgVpvgF1xRpRM-YY0Bpob4kiVfft-FZVu9EnfPTJgP3zTJxhb41yqbUYPiaDX0_ctOzwhrWhcSyHxl5ve96csAFDGE/s3064/DSC05020.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiIXX9csavauQWsLdR0qrVZZEQ2RpXqk_m17ShQSpKYOoL_G7m_9clcIpNbCFd3hsnAQ83SmlllCTVf8qnnu25Uds1GTnGXmPLdnRgVpvgF1xRpRM-YY0Bpob4kiVfft-FZVu9EnfPTJgP3zTJxhb41yqbUYPiaDX0_ctOzwhrWhcSyHxl5ve96csAFDGE/s600/DSC05020.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲【衣櫃擴充】這是一張雙面明信片的其中一面</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">《矮人礦坑》：第一個連接衣櫃與起點的矮人，將自己的矮人卡與遊戲設置時放一旁的矮人卡更換。</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">《矮人礦坑２》：第一個連接衣櫃與起點的矮人，將自己的矮人卡換成矮人卡牌庫頂那張，然後原本的矮人卡放到牌庫最下方。</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjieMxWOU0zz2m-QGx8MarXNz96QnVeMKPtT_nn2bhbPv57O6CyjjGzUNKwAwkAVQPSTklRGEvP2us2n6du2470GDmUXT1tMMvxMMOU9lsyD00EJiFePjAAfTH8-8WYtjcoRf2CuseuHyQN3MKaablifggpxn4hIYUASwvJNqr0Nz450tyrlTMjNUWyu0Y/s3888/DSC05021.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjieMxWOU0zz2m-QGx8MarXNz96QnVeMKPtT_nn2bhbPv57O6CyjjGzUNKwAwkAVQPSTklRGEvP2us2n6du2470GDmUXT1tMMvxMMOU9lsyD00EJiFePjAAfTH8-8WYtjcoRf2CuseuHyQN3MKaablifggpxn4hIYUASwvJNqr0Nz450tyrlTMjNUWyu0Y/s600/DSC05021.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲卡片共有四包</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh2KS3CDXee7E3lJXrjmUiFd2U8mBb6BzGQiXT4h57cs3QD9rH_aMVNCjRji5B1okYXfMKcz63p-iq70wdsEnqUbaspVOdibMSm69HWY5-Wunk2iaATgx9kDiIlms0jQK4aV4yxW5tU1mo826PECSnS-SXTem1dZ3GhhhkuON_0ZcRvKCNO0jH3SIkMMjk/s5068/DSC05022.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh2KS3CDXee7E3lJXrjmUiFd2U8mBb6BzGQiXT4h57cs3QD9rH_aMVNCjRji5B1okYXfMKcz63p-iq70wdsEnqUbaspVOdibMSm69HWY5-Wunk2iaATgx9kDiIlms0jQK4aV4yxW5tU1mo826PECSnS-SXTem1dZ3GhhhkuON_0ZcRvKCNO0jH3SIkMMjk/s600/DSC05022.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲這邊分別是《矮人礦坑》與《矮人礦坑２》的卡片～我就不一一拍照了～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgLT03O5BIQdZsvQnu6TQz1NM4inSkkO5TIeHvfbuXH0Wz-7wHXRqZayevkOPEgAdwUVlDnb_BmGy3otq0TDHp_McZvFa4leOcLg67voQ6I9xPYF1NZpzNy1xwZkNQaauRBOeS6Wg96at-lbOeytoTvyZ_nO8iLRjtucZfCA3Sd-wrCy-RD05AvMiMKpIo/s5132/DSC05023.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgLT03O5BIQdZsvQnu6TQz1NM4inSkkO5TIeHvfbuXH0Wz-7wHXRqZayevkOPEgAdwUVlDnb_BmGy3otq0TDHp_McZvFa4leOcLg67voQ6I9xPYF1NZpzNy1xwZkNQaauRBOeS6Wg96at-lbOeytoTvyZ_nO8iLRjtucZfCA3Sd-wrCy-RD05AvMiMKpIo/s600/DSC05023.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲《矮人礦坑２》的卡片左下有明顯的【２】所以很好區分</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEifjQxdOK3EaIJtRsTMMIMOYvW9-gyinmBg2mkxnKW1arxzbcQxsizZdlaopbapOGHon-gI0go19Jfim1Aornv5nKRi7IZDDCKP4i3JG4gqK7bZ00H_fCDn3wfoNF5LreISHF1yF_OaKs96BEmO0DvFFFzvlOS54Gbarh-y6J1t4W5uS42M5aCPC-Us1Us/s5072/DSC05024.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEifjQxdOK3EaIJtRsTMMIMOYvW9-gyinmBg2mkxnKW1arxzbcQxsizZdlaopbapOGHon-gI0go19Jfim1Aornv5nKRi7IZDDCKP4i3JG4gqK7bZ00H_fCDn3wfoNF5LreISHF1yF_OaKs96BEmO0DvFFFzvlOS54Gbarh-y6J1t4W5uS42M5aCPC-Us1Us/s600/DSC05024.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲９張世界盃特殊卡（２０１６－２０２３）！老實說光是這幾張卡片就已經整盒回本又賺翻了！我上網去查過，這些卡片有的根本就已經買不到，有些就算能買到，每張至少也要５歐元到１０歐元～簡直就是夢幻逸品～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong><em>【２０１６　自私鬼（２張）】</em></strong></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">只能搭配基本版遊戲，設置時將自私鬼取代１名淘金矮人，其餘玩法不變。分發金塊時，自私鬼必須自己連接到最後的寶藏卡才能獲勝，並獲得４個金塊，否則本輪只會兩手空空回家。錦標賽模式才會用到２張自私鬼。</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong><em>【２０１７　交換終點】</em></strong></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">打出此牌後，在不檢視的情況下選擇兩張終點牌，並做出類似洗牌的動作，接著放回兩張終點，這下全場只有你知道，這兩個鐘點是否有交換。</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong><em>【２０１８　藏寶庫】</em></strong></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">打出此牌之後，不從牌庫頂抽牌，改由從棄牌堆頂端抽５張牌，然後選１張保留。</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong><em>【２０１９　否決！】</em></strong></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">在其他玩家的回合，當他打出路徑卡或是行動卡之後，打出否決！接著將該玩家的卡片還有否決卡一起放進棄牌堆，你們兩個人都從牌庫頂補充１張牌～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong><em>【２０２０　逆轉順位】</em></strong></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">打出此牌之後，遊戲的回合順位立刻逆轉執行～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong><em>【２０２１　工藝大師】</em></strong></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">工藝大師可以修理任何東西，移除１張工具損壞卡。</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong><em>【２０２２　探索者】</em></strong></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">打出此牌之後，可以接著先後打出２張路徑卡，回合結束之後補２張牌。（也就是你的手牌之後會少１張。</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong><em>【２０２３　改道】</em></strong></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">將最後放進迷宮的那張路徑卡移動至新的位置，但能必須要符合放置規則。</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEimyGANyk2WfLerkUkN2MmMyhah5rdDokjjJtoiC9v0LQGBVzJWf0Tg5dmuP1kRpeRZuDUJHLIhG3Aq_eJQkwyg2oxcZvVTMAqnrUjWkJPcpSbNWxWkzu00Z-OewshX_qu4z8I8NaNT0QKNY2tQVswFX625OzQzuJuYIybYewSdWklc9JFImxQD2KwgjK8/s4804/DSC05025.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEimyGANyk2WfLerkUkN2MmMyhah5rdDokjjJtoiC9v0LQGBVzJWf0Tg5dmuP1kRpeRZuDUJHLIhG3Aq_eJQkwyg2oxcZvVTMAqnrUjWkJPcpSbNWxWkzu00Z-OewshX_qu4z8I8NaNT0QKNY2tQVswFX625OzQzuJuYIybYewSdWklc9JFImxQD2KwgjK8/s600/DSC05025.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲新的寶箱擴充：遊戲設置時，將這個擴充所有的路徑卡洗牌，抽出４張隨機放進迷宮中，但都不能相鄰。接著洗牌擴充中所有的寶箱卡，一樣抽出４張面朝下蓋在剛剛的路徑卡上方。當有玩家把路徑連接到這個位置的時候，先打開路徑卡，並按照正常規則將路徑卡放置到原先蓋著的位置上，接著才打開寶藏卡並執行寶箱卡效果。最後將寶箱卡放到一旁。</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEi5UXARd2V4daQk6JQ-ZfeuQCXi3fKVQ5-HnmZNN5iUMFGeGeOQCcDHg-fncA1uB-TTM5j3D2PuxGRJ5cLzYuuMzIUUXlHBwfcr92mwh7NVvy8ycZtAQnYxi_25nD9m8i1uNndalqY-JK5xEI1SWayWpiNw0ljkNHQVWRCKJA6WL_0LrIuIXgOHwxfezBw/s4056/DSC05026.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEi5UXARd2V4daQk6JQ-ZfeuQCXi3fKVQ5-HnmZNN5iUMFGeGeOQCcDHg-fncA1uB-TTM5j3D2PuxGRJ5cLzYuuMzIUUXlHBwfcr92mwh7NVvy8ycZtAQnYxi_25nD9m8i1uNndalqY-JK5xEI1SWayWpiNw0ljkNHQVWRCKJA6WL_0LrIuIXgOHwxfezBw/s600/DSC05026.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲新的終點擴充：這個會直接取代原本的終點卡，設置的時候把有寶藏（金塊）的那一張先拿起來，其他７張洗牌之後隨機抽取４張。加入基本終點卡之後，將５張終點卡洗勻後按照說明書的指示設置成新的終點～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEjJHRinde55qUrX4zRGsmKuTBRnfzngT5liWp-mPSWGeCDpMpMZi3sXk2wr4-sGxceiOr5ZZrcqTE1OpQd1FLtM84XGAjhgoMlQPvd_QtpPZfsi8wBdSi7rBhHcS5MbaOH4WBN128uX0gglb4jVc3-TVUv_HKcA7vMugvCt7wv6dIjc2uOV9i1kAQnQ_Bc\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>真愛無誤！</strong></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">《Saboteur 矮人礦坑》的好玩我應該不需要再贅述了～除了還不太會說謊的小朋友，我找不到不適合玩矮人礦坑的族群～當年我剛開始瘋桌遊的時候就是帶著它從北到南的跑，親戚朋友幾乎是只要看到人就會被我推坑這一款的程度～總之，《Saboteur 矮人礦坑》的確是我的真愛無誤～但不知道是不是對一代的愛太深，後來出了《矮人礦坑２》雖然也是有玩，但總覺得還是比較喜歡原汁原味的設計～加上越來越多新品的轟炸，也就慢慢淡忘了這款遊戲～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">這次二十週年還能重拾這款遊戲真的很感動，裡面大大小小的擴充給的非常有誠意，也都讓遊戲可以有更多變化，一次讓你把兩代矮人還有擴充都收好收滿，更棒的是你完全不用擔心牌背會有色差的問題～畢竟都是同一批一起印刷的～我真心找不到不收這一款的理由～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">缺點．．．．嗯～這款遊戲如果有缺點，那就是我的缺點了（千錯萬錯都是我的錯！）！總之，雖然時間過去這麼多年，但以派對遊戲來說，《Saboteur 矮人礦坑》絕對還是我心目中頂點中的頂點！沒玩過這款經典遊戲的朋友真心推薦一定要嘗試看看！目前天鵝正在做早鳥預購，<a href=\"https://www.swanpanasia.com/promo/saboteur-20th-preorder\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">我把網址放在這邊喔～</a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgASLyC8gh_9bwF9cZk1tx29klGqeGj02BtdQfIWT1G1tkrh3nPBkc7EVbjMlTljzGbLOG1TOiFlbnrAKgjHEgGmVHeQS0nQPootMARMlRcwK54TycPrbNN3l-NQz6cKeZPjUA81IQugToAWkjW2eY1edaLBZRH68Oqxg-lIrwSx_r2M5Dn1IlvhNYvsdg/s4981/DSC05028.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgASLyC8gh_9bwF9cZk1tx29klGqeGj02BtdQfIWT1G1tkrh3nPBkc7EVbjMlTljzGbLOG1TOiFlbnrAKgjHEgGmVHeQS0nQPootMARMlRcwK54TycPrbNN3l-NQz6cKeZPjUA81IQugToAWkjW2eY1edaLBZRH68Oqxg-lIrwSx_r2M5Dn1IlvhNYvsdg/s600/DSC05028.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲遊戲收納照，很可惜的是沒有給牌套空間</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhOc9spP5yh2i4mCtLh6Z13NYRq024Yf53m0-DdJbKC4NY3I5PRcMr3yIJJ8U1HrBjzXj0XniDrbah7PuDJzeq12geQBWnEKDLUKGVS8NoyZz6H2XEPFlUq2RaQCHG_WiOnvNw-8aQFX5CkgGS8LKpn6KDcH_CGE21aVi5-LgM5opSpoOFL6YwTKI5ruk0/s4184/DSC05029.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhOc9spP5yh2i4mCtLh6Z13NYRq024Yf53m0-DdJbKC4NY3I5PRcMr3yIJJ8U1HrBjzXj0XniDrbah7PuDJzeq12geQBWnEKDLUKGVS8NoyZz6H2XEPFlUq2RaQCHG_WiOnvNw-8aQFX5CkgGS8LKpn6KDcH_CGE21aVi5-LgM5opSpoOFL6YwTKI5ruk0/s600/DSC05029.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲遊戲收納照２</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEj_YMIqQsjtNp8Vhazdw-SOGRl4x45WzlHdZH8JYQU1RmB7EqVLWYBBHW69oDuFZ1Qc-7VMEuHZDZqgz1HhskrvpjzeI4pjE6N1YlAIhqbamHPxJdNiMJ69XweYA5rhCEl_eKzLerfDAF2s4fig0jx2FVTjYg8Ryq7WtqFFbt20li2aQuUSefVJsJwbxtM/s4568/DSC05030.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEj_YMIqQsjtNp8Vhazdw-SOGRl4x45WzlHdZH8JYQU1RmB7EqVLWYBBHW69oDuFZ1Qc-7VMEuHZDZqgz1HhskrvpjzeI4pjE6N1YlAIhqbamHPxJdNiMJ69XweYA5rhCEl_eKzLerfDAF2s4fig0jx2FVTjYg8Ryq7WtqFFbt20li2aQuUSefVJsJwbxtM/s600/DSC05030.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲這次的紀念版還有送一條專屬的桌遊比基尼～</p><p><br></p>', '2024-11-18 10:20:51', '2024-11-18 10:20:51', 1, 'forum-1731896451320-158862017.jpg'),
(15, 1, '【桌遊開箱報】Master Sinseh 蓋世中醫 開箱+介紹', '<h3><br></h3><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEguHJebLDEGfSy4CVN0sRg6CazHZ3bF-rqjcaY37w5QNEJyFUtHeJTV-ogsGP9rs-lAhJuYdIUAQW7y-gHEULKVSx6lmWvBsr1EK6sT9IY6JwiGAdxNMjnlOE3KBEfUSrca23QOlQlo0g0MkbL9SOPWkMIVT2JjLuK4mFI27zgC4FW7PKdLgtjWSXlSsoM/s2284/DSC04964.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEguHJebLDEGfSy4CVN0sRg6CazHZ3bF-rqjcaY37w5QNEJyFUtHeJTV-ogsGP9rs-lAhJuYdIUAQW7y-gHEULKVSx6lmWvBsr1EK6sT9IY6JwiGAdxNMjnlOE3KBEfUSrca23QOlQlo0g0MkbL9SOPWkMIVT2JjLuK4mFI27zgC4FW7PKdLgtjWSXlSsoM/s600/DSC04964.JPG\"></a></p><p><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEjMoWKkAa-bY3lmaH5qwZehv5kGP9vL2XvSD7FV7OXGxz2QFTsAm22rnsYb6QqqgdBh-HPdDYMWSntPeehnS-Do2FDnkY_e3-KjGI0xLV5GCHGnqrm9jdNlU5lXiWjFIQdNC5IK3McESGw6nfmOSOYc1PeAAgSjt6I_pnjyF5DMK9c_DFTwBMx1V6fOxV8\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">在《Master Sinseh 蓋世中醫》中，我們將扮演醫術高超的中醫師，在江湖之中懸壺濟世，解決患者們的問題～但故事的劇情就是你想的那樣沒錯，就是這麼剛好，也有一群醫術跟你一樣高超的中醫師，也要來懸壺濟世了！這下看來除了要把病人看好之外，還要跟同業競爭哩～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEj-XYIv3kJn33d5J8DcqO7t5ugh1CgZvfoFqenPf-7dkWiNDG8k8z9s5O7g7YbfLHt67nVFSz7T2QUkwBO2BKM420AUnajlaxAl1DPPx1y3CZs0THGPLKXmB6PtX2UHZdWy2ZlV6qZEPfAKhJWKFf7hl3C-T81_nZhOJTcHIjyQq1jhgVp_l494SayY178\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEguHJebLDEGfSy4CVN0sRg6CazHZ3bF-rqjcaY37w5QNEJyFUtHeJTV-ogsGP9rs-lAhJuYdIUAQW7y-gHEULKVSx6lmWvBsr1EK6sT9IY6JwiGAdxNMjnlOE3KBEfUSrca23QOlQlo0g0MkbL9SOPWkMIVT2JjLuK4mFI27zgC4FW7PKdLgtjWSXlSsoM/s2284/DSC04964.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEguHJebLDEGfSy4CVN0sRg6CazHZ3bF-rqjcaY37w5QNEJyFUtHeJTV-ogsGP9rs-lAhJuYdIUAQW7y-gHEULKVSx6lmWvBsr1EK6sT9IY6JwiGAdxNMjnlOE3KBEfUSrca23QOlQlo0g0Mk