9vZ2xl/AVvXsEiTc6SkjvCS7DsrvZK5i82CVYWmYPFa9n9ccxyStJuBZFlcEMuai5KPGCWOi7ntF0DFN2wtUTJ85pF9LzQH8d8JnkWX0GrrIe-2nEqshXIlYk0ArTgCsDWtyjdHUtyN-vp3N9CkHV5zLY-8HkV0larC05JFwx8ugnfwz4qjzX_crBs1hmU4H0ecvBk4L_M/s600/DSC04970.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲卡片兩包</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjfMZ6VbCfrIlmnzV4mZ9w6EyCf8z7uV4d4wZ6NHPXeuhkMsRck2WmMACY1YssLSioWV_C58nPpoQr4T-1H68QR6MhzR3Rn1BE_XyQ_8HvexYlncqaweFIo6yNpJv6kaPRlYAMdBBC51BEST4YH6dts0fhFCZ7zCSCDkyIB8vnLQXTZ4HdojejnE-YIamU/s4660/DSC04971.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjfMZ6VbCfrIlmnzV4mZ9w6EyCf8z7uV4d4wZ6NHPXeuhkMsRck2WmMACY1YssLSioWV_C58nPpoQr4T-1H68QR6MhzR3Rn1BE_XyQ_8HvexYlncqaweFIo6yNpJv6kaPRlYAMdBBC51BEST4YH6dts0fhFCZ7zCSCDkyIB8vnLQXTZ4HdojejnE-YIamU/s600/DSC04971.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲卡片可以分為三類</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjSyOEFa3F0ZiJ0EKXwo3SOU4gWW0QNNllytszqrDIWvazu5tw6X0KhuSHmk-ZvWS1JRn-1Zj7IjYa8hDOu5tcG3oW6uyWlH3KK4V-xaESD25Misu3ZyJ8E1sNSxHUZfZPt1WfyBNSIqU1_4w7AQuVKkDQ7gAjmBMx0fr6G6lIyGNXp7BaIp4ltqrJRmbI/s5104/DSC04972.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjSyOEFa3F0ZiJ0EKXwo3SOU4gWW0QNNllytszqrDIWvazu5tw6X0KhuSHmk-ZvWS1JRn-1Zj7IjYa8hDOu5tcG3oW6uyWlH3KK4V-xaESD25Misu3ZyJ8E1sNSxHUZfZPt1WfyBNSIqU1_4w7AQuVKkDQ7gAjmBMx0fr6G6lIyGNXp7BaIp4ltqrJRmbI/s600/DSC04972.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲第一類是玩家手牌，粉紅、咖啡、綠、黃、藍，以上五種顏色分別是五位玩家的專屬顏色（手牌）。紫色的為特殊卡，想加入擴充規則的時候才會用它～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgjwnMqrlMMjiqKjCzuEannnQQ5fLvC5-b2JO7jVhl4edPxxaNieIhwBdHAXZKr43ICdjU59grncHuDNsC0iCxo5ni6Vew-ua0VUBdNRimxnVbqndlFZkG2V0MHSOEIfi5DIfFGeFMIbSPHqkW0vULca-G_Cti-Az31_OC_h9XgnJBt9pFLn4XypTUu82o/s3484/DSC04973.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgjwnMqrlMMjiqKjCzuEannnQQ5fLvC5-b2JO7jVhl4edPxxaNieIhwBdHAXZKr43ICdjU59grncHuDNsC0iCxo5ni6Vew-ua0VUBdNRimxnVbqndlFZkG2V0MHSOEIfi5DIfFGeFMIbSPHqkW0vULca-G_Cti-Az31_OC_h9XgnJBt9pFLn4XypTUu82o/s600/DSC04973.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲玩家們的手牌就是各種不同的治療藥物，每種藥物都有不同的療效</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">遊戲中藥物使用之後就會棄置，但有４張【甘草】上面有一個返回手中的符號，使用過後不會不見，會從回你的手中，所以每回合都還是可以使用（但效果當然比較差）。</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">＊其中有一張甘草符號有錯誤，但只要一開始就講清楚，是不會影響遊玩的～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEi4_OgQDXFi-RzTXx58eRTL6zUpUDYH2KWXeIyNonBl7ukm0bzDt8A3g7qomQ2vFylJhW7aQ44jc6CGMoTINniiHHxnMGSiq1ZTC5zzRnxRgY2X3Ed37mSsgWja-4EWDN3pfV2peIsTtWmaX4Cwv94wftieCSuwd5etxGcp4G67GPfcuCYNA89Sz0iGLKo/s3448/DSC04974.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEi4_OgQDXFi-RzTXx58eRTL6zUpUDYH2KWXeIyNonBl7ukm0bzDt8A3g7qomQ2vFylJhW7aQ44jc6CGMoTINniiHHxnMGSiq1ZTC5zzRnxRgY2X3Ed37mSsgWja-4EWDN3pfV2peIsTtWmaX4Cwv94wftieCSuwd5etxGcp4G67GPfcuCYNA89Sz0iGLKo/s600/DSC04974.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲紫色的為特殊卡，想加入擴充規則的時候才會用它～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjHHbzExUGGtI2pyW5AZegOZ7Cwu0Os_UbIEgf41G_MFGoUGR5LSMhDHZkMomjJrPOv62ZOU0110FMwoQqIBxN6rwTFt8yFFTfe8WwcpdDVu4C-NrQU5sL9yV1Pe3MwfgpIM0E_hGKwO_gVrwaVbcl487SjSPqFoHt6oZIq3YNrb3lugJPEuYpEsDeWmBY/s4568/DSC04975.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjHHbzExUGGtI2pyW5AZegOZ7Cwu0Os_UbIEgf41G_MFGoUGR5LSMhDHZkMomjJrPOv62ZOU0110FMwoQqIBxN6rwTFt8yFFTfe8WwcpdDVu4C-NrQU5sL9yV1Pe3MwfgpIM0E_hGKwO_gVrwaVbcl487SjSPqFoHt6oZIq3YNrb3lugJPEuYpEsDeWmBY/s600/DSC04975.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲第二種卡片為書本，書本裡面有各式各樣不同的獎勵</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjRkUPdSi7d-ZdL0hgo6TaJUytn9fjMO1pnUoD6-d23yNNsBNA0XbEOt4A3qKBBxZ0Ahh2_Xqz6pyMSik0jRqEC5vvtif85PRQGPTJ17qXyg7gJ2u8v4WFFo5xLdfsWZYK_TGl_zwEj0jRJCs2ELJfyk99SClLZ0mVrWhfwk1G-zciZB5OzX5DRjTSTXu0/s4696/DSC04976.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjRkUPdSi7d-ZdL0hgo6TaJUytn9fjMO1pnUoD6-d23yNNsBNA0XbEOt4A3qKBBxZ0Ahh2_Xqz6pyMSik0jRqEC5vvtif85PRQGPTJ17qXyg7gJ2u8v4WFFo5xLdfsWZYK_TGl_zwEj0jRJCs2ELJfyk99SClLZ0mVrWhfwk1G-zciZB5OzX5DRjTSTXu0/s600/DSC04976.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲第三種卡片則是病患，每位病患下方都有標示適合治療他們的方向。左上角的愛心是得分，有的病患還會送你仁、善、德的符號（遊戲結束會有成套蒐集分數）。</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEhJ4_aghNvyQ-cdKmQXMeIbqrgRWpwmFaJWAM7xl7LNbEHZoOt5JQYNdlfIh-Y2vclQZBX7Y25AvxeBbVWYl_-BoF0zLB38lzv8vfVkvDfBRMneESc6tVV1bwb5fL-gaZ18cy0__pcbJ-RXr3qz_sm4c29-YB9OJ6NFyZWtaWqACgpjeo941T69j9s9fCA\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲規則不難，我們讓龍龍來教你！</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEiYbh5ZNhgL3QWxTiO9ZKf4jv95tgiXvjsaqGl30jCUqgwJyk5onnPX739IRgNXS69jmtVDTGwDWXaylhxyYz2shhCchboJrExzfnllNXFseSKo2uc14FU7HKZ3gx9uF0HoIQgkny2zOFODXOOC4lD2Wx7Fdlqg2SPdgwHqkSh97Sb61LhZFVTUuHq0aVI\"></p><p><br></p><p><strong>望聞問切！</strong></p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">中醫是一門很高深的學問，是幾千年來先人們經驗累積的成果，但在《Master Sinseh 蓋世中醫》中，中醫變得沒有那麼遙不可及～原本需要好多年的臨床經驗才能正確判斷出的病人病症，在遊戲中通通都被簡化了，取而代之的是我們可以很輕易判斷該怎麼治療，才能達到最佳的療效～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">但，在藥材的運用上就要看一些運氣與手腕了。雖然遊戲中沒有競標的環節，但其實偷偷藏有競標的要素，對於每一回合開出來的三個病人，到底要用多少的資源，多大的力氣去救治。是該保留實力，讓自己之後有更強力的藥材可以運用？還是該搶得先機，有幾個就救幾個？治療的過程還蠻爾虞我詐的，有些病患治療值要衝超高才能搶到，有些病患卻莫名其妙大家都沒有特效藥可以醫他，治療值很低的玩家就可以帶走～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">這款遊戲不吃文字，但會需要用到簡單的加減乘除，所以我會推薦給家裡有小學生的家庭玩家、想要支援五人派對遊戲的玩家、想要懸壺濟世或是神農嘗百草的玩家～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjtPtXP2AI2cU4FpH4rMd1f2q71ZcTwFdgPLqZ1xocXMv2CtaWkQOnOoWAP_uUURuOqRH_alSSRg3YgZqNdtL3K3rfHv7DxDbUXCyZdXcgNy5CRdsQR3T65jO9hRodPtv3Lny80yNnVY74nL5jY6w-3mAsi1XeOCsc0Eokv19hTl-gPrWwQL4WLZAlqqMg/s4224/DSC04977.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjtPtXP2AI2cU4FpH4rMd1f2q71ZcTwFdgPLqZ1xocXMv2CtaWkQOnOoWAP_uUURuOqRH_alSSRg3YgZqNdtL3K3rfHv7DxDbUXCyZdXcgNy5CRdsQR3T65jO9hRodPtv3Lny80yNnVY74nL5jY6w-3mAsi1XeOCsc0Eokv19hTl-gPrWwQL4WLZAlqqMg/s600/DSC04977.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲遊戲收納照</p><p><br></p>', '2024-11-18 10:25:17', '2024-11-18 10:25:17', 1, 'forum-1731896717448-654170972.jpg'),
(16, 1, '【桌遊開箱報】Shop until you drop Lah! 瞎拼袋禍日 開箱+介紹', '<h3><br></h3><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEisKtJFSQNZujWCbpDof81Q1vhqV9kY-d1-80WZacLnTzj7_y0-qiV7MyVirmB1YWD27Com18uMiANnUkwh9HNVqqHR2NeDlG0V1G9DKY5E-IgX7LZu5u7Id-Zv7O7N6_y6heTAdPaEERSm8kHpPVEwW8qrxNTRRedvaYfB8smIdnNz6hfd8lornsZf9b0/w478-h640/DSC04948.JPG\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEjMoWKkAa-bY3lmaH5qwZehv5kGP9vL2XvSD7FV7OXGxz2QFTsAm22rnsYb6QqqgdBh-HPdDYMWSntPeehnS-Do2FDnkY_e3-KjGI0xLV5GCHGnqrm9jdNlU5lXiWjFIQdNC5IK3McESGw6nfmOSOYc1PeAAgSjt6I_pnjyF5DMK9c_DFTwBMx1V6fOxV8\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">新加坡最大的Shopping折扣季開跑啦！Mr. Kiasu（怕輸）是1990年代新加坡相當受歡迎的卡通人物，也是本次遊戲的主角。我們將扮演一群到百貨商場瘋狂血拼的民眾，角色都相當的有個性，有的怕輸、有的怕死、有的愛美、也有的愛吃～是一款相當歡樂的購物遊戲，重點是！這款遊戲的美編是我們的桌遊芩畫！我還不推爆！</p><p><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEj-XYIv3kJn33d5J8DcqO7t5ugh1CgZvfoFqenPf-7dkWiNDG8k8z9s5O7g7YbfLHt67nVFSz7T2QUkwBO2BKM420AUnajlaxAl1DPPx1y3CZs0THGPLKXmB6PtX2UHZdWy2ZlV6qZEPfAKhJWKFf7hl3C-T81_nZhOJTcHIjyQq1jhgVp_l494SayY178\"></p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEieMhpHJAR_31DDB56RTvQtYOZ9AFPLsDjkYlgb003ZjK_sXcvC2-wFNCJ_BzjwwklWPwzx5izNbJnQOrSHZAVafjP95mgHIIaVhznwEmb4LaWdoX5BQZq9X-T2C9MT346qLedehL_jwm1Vm-D_xOTv0uhWjhdTX_BdZm6xVjH9H1kjQAQQ5D9Cy_94jQg/w478-h640/DSC04948.JPG\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲封面可以看到各種鮮明可愛的人物</p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiVUdm7OZdAqn50665zimjR-SJl9ABJICFabLVak9ciRBqEFpQ2eqc6C-E7SduArmcUEvKMKPYlyFjDhronLMKHeELPdpWPqYYuYhf2sL3LFr4Vu4MoRkaCc3FXRjNj4L-dIpHznO9M3ulMZwGQYIXmSxUgvomOIz-9ql5N0MQhisZDDErfIJbMFpDg2k8/w640-h402/DSC04949.JPG\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲遊戲人數：2-5人　建議年齡：7+　遊戲時間：20-30 mins</p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgwm_hUU_GJIcFf7qKnY764-vkfNZ5IZsaVdGDq5Wnt3oLJymLVYF15uSlIH7gHzmTF5a9nfjjiIOQrtNUxS9L9rAjKzokR-5RyKsHOaNdyesUHPUkkU6WZAgxtm0aQJZzlE9OxS2H2HQ2mdSgUBMLQy_uGq0zJR6a4KA_TPg3E0Dq8RWBFg4g6bPWOsuQ/w474-h640/DSC04950.JPG\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲背面可以看到遊戲樣貌</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEji7tMfZGQiNJO4ayniXoE4s99Ap375dUlgMjNCP22GaIhjskHSvqZL86ZGlB7AHoOwxGzNH_PltTSuYBgRBrke-bkqbaYG2GA0_UzDnr_gqV9KzQYAUfmz1ZKwwj5l0KRo6Gj-s-6D3bXYdlIMviPtLShruaEPMkCLF_bCVon5hQO5bHBPCq-6Q852REk/s4260/DSC04951.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEji7tMfZGQiNJO4ayniXoE4s99Ap375dUlgMjNCP22GaIhjskHSvqZL86ZGlB7AHoOwxGzNH_PltTSuYBgRBrke-bkqbaYG2GA0_UzDnr_gqV9KzQYAUfmz1ZKwwj5l0KRo6Gj-s-6D3bXYdlIMviPtLShruaEPMkCLF_bCVon5hQO5bHBPCq-6Q852REk/s600/DSC04951.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲內容物一覽</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgn_htzeDXLP586NR1u40TuTr040D4mElg7MLgs8zZYczkk5Mgw5TezGeMVbf4MHcjtyH5AIQUW0rsk8Jrrf4OBCqIsuYm_X5sKtL94r_ekbkKFaOMzDK1nHvcR28CnJuDLNb-YEI22yUlLqtvywqKOJdoAHKPJuTZPGr9J1Hn1L5rF5RMLC_p5Fo1t8Fw/s600/DSC04953.JPG\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲說明書有英文跟中文兩種語言</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjQU2i6WoWk4nzebvtarcQkXWrjfcR934JQMS6_rlDpWpsT1g8iKak1XEdWNd-LgOd6SiRD5GNA24hnW9uYrVTETsLvzrUVDlN6Pv3ZviC8GGADo2_TzUXwDWBbvPlZkOnb-k-98p5yLqm1SqrsK6wz09Vn9xRyWDn_0lvbsRTsmzpgqQvPi6ZrHLUjYVI/s4840/DSC04952.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjQU2i6WoWk4nzebvtarcQkXWrjfcR934JQMS6_rlDpWpsT1g8iKak1XEdWNd-LgOd6SiRD5GNA24hnW9uYrVTETsLvzrUVDlN6Pv3ZviC8GGADo2_TzUXwDWBbvPlZkOnb-k-98p5yLqm1SqrsK6wz09Vn9xRyWDn_0lvbsRTsmzpgqQvPi6ZrHLUjYVI/s600/DSC04952.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲卡片有兩種尺寸</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEj1SninCubuNL0hcrPTdHj4Hm-nXj4aFQ9SyXhIPw15Ml61Zjw2VHW65hk2_BS-VA3xSzSTzw7qMfT-H720oX18AaPECmDekZQ94TWbyyRjxvBilcbVi9DsEBdZZdzQJE75JpmXvcjhp9fcCYtkRklOEsx1eC6iktGv6wgiUGaTgRJbDgitfTLQoIv61hc/s3573/DSC04954.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEj1SninCubuNL0hcrPTdHj4Hm-nXj4aFQ9SyXhIPw15Ml61Zjw2VHW65hk2_BS-VA3xSzSTzw7qMfT-H720oX18AaPECmDekZQ94TWbyyRjxvBilcbVi9DsEBdZZdzQJE75JpmXvcjhp9fcCYtkRklOEsx1eC6iktGv6wgiUGaTgRJbDgitfTLQoIv61hc/s600/DSC04954.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲大張卡片就是五位主角</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">（一面有特殊能力，另一面沒有）</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEif6ME9LetvZwvdIU93AUl964Sn3hkviC-RVcxPZfo7DydXMAEozSl9tHz96SqfPPZYYPgfLr4o2Ebe5KwHffIyBbiTIcVfb0zCTbnm8E9sDpFCWuHoyyiDWPsC6_CZJV5bNldiB9flX0Vhhl9OFpQPbuKG6i79rdBeIYwCRFsdSOc1zJUQQ6jKafH7mcM/s3928/DSC04955.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEif6ME9LetvZwvdIU93AUl964Sn3hkviC-RVcxPZfo7DydXMAEozSl9tHz96SqfPPZYYPgfLr4o2Ebe5KwHffIyBbiTIcVfb0zCTbnm8E9sDpFCWuHoyyiDWPsC6_CZJV5bNldiB9flX0Vhhl9OFpQPbuKG6i79rdBeIYwCRFsdSOc1zJUQQ6jKafH7mcM/s600/DSC04955.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲小張卡片就是各種折扣商品，還有代購的任務卡</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjg9hWUTunZHVfuZhsH01p-JCGLfEysW_JsPRxIPAVVPS16dM7UT0Oho8nKyuk7x7zIa8SnWAgX7kVL8LADc6n7EZM2Cg8eTzs7hGzJxYx1YA4Eqj-FPtZMTNssppiBKz8sgkp_K4_yeTnRTgAwE0q7-oD20xUF-0zhP5OieIXCF_PqusZvBgGM2fn6uOM/s5472/DSC04956.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjg9hWUTunZHVfuZhsH01p-JCGLfEysW_JsPRxIPAVVPS16dM7UT0Oho8nKyuk7x7zIa8SnWAgX7kVL8LADc6n7EZM2Cg8eTzs7hGzJxYx1YA4Eqj-FPtZMTNssppiBKz8sgkp_K4_yeTnRTgAwE0q7-oD20xUF-0zhP5OieIXCF_PqusZvBgGM2fn6uOM/s600/DSC04956.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲小卡片的牌背很好看，很有特賣會的感覺！</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEh7khaa2vSPXkvTe9SfouowddjCtYFhLSxwn-_1dvg7tJqC2K1S9tAkcpEeWjOR9ufSSr1sgKeioRuC8Rzk94mor1CGAqRlpj-c2gPVzYHbFA26ktfAXJZs6lT-q6eUxMSQmkYL9llZRKaj3iXINJDpujQo0fnkoYDsO80Q5EiK0Dwv4Va3iby4sUpFZS0\"></p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲一樣先放龍龍的影片</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhINRvD2U7wAWhO_NmSBRU7fp8sFaYYIJ3zqBE-HEqpsW_-sddCfprcq_EB-CBh7eC-PYMOzyN-O7neC8d-xzn8l4nIsUZfqCWEtCrD0sFdsN_803-p37jjJVmVvVyOjyJWdcbvd-qPiOg5JjyusuRKckePJYNke8P3CITBxBM8vLh9o8qv0SbjAvvjubc/s5128/DSC04957.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhINRvD2U7wAWhO_NmSBRU7fp8sFaYYIJ3zqBE-HEqpsW_-sddCfprcq_EB-CBh7eC-PYMOzyN-O7neC8d-xzn8l4nIsUZfqCWEtCrD0sFdsN_803-p37jjJVmVvVyOjyJWdcbvd-qPiOg5JjyusuRKckePJYNke8P3CITBxBM8vLh9o8qv0SbjAvvjubc/s600/DSC04957.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲遊戲設置很簡單，每人選一個角色，將所有手牌洗混之後形成牌堆並翻出人數＋１張卡片形成展示區～這樣就算設置完成了～（起始玩家可隨機決定，或是讓最近看過漫畫的人當起始玩家）</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEin78EXlsnYiFByb6euPZZ_VngmRS7tn-vdpD-CNrf2GJXYI29FEB7qIUmpJBtQVPSHlM5UESGU8D3-vGpCE7SmBg_PK4pbSUosbw8mBpX-72lvlmXR-QfttQEm_e2nAbddGhMp6PpH3TyoTUj662nkZSVeCiFHdU_yL3raHIOQqMv1TbnAYM7q8as5iCM/s3112/DSC04958.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEin78EXlsnYiFByb6euPZZ_VngmRS7tn-vdpD-CNrf2GJXYI29FEB7qIUmpJBtQVPSHlM5UESGU8D3-vGpCE7SmBg_PK4pbSUosbw8mBpX-72lvlmXR-QfttQEm_e2nAbddGhMp6PpH3TyoTUj662nkZSVeCiFHdU_yL3raHIOQqMv1TbnAYM7q8as5iCM/s600/DSC04958.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲由起始玩家開始，大家輪流從展示區拿取一張卡片，如果是商品卡，就像這樣放進自己的袋子中。每位角色都有三個袋子，分別在角色卡的上方、左方跟右方。接著把沒人要的那張卡片棄掉，重新翻出人數＋１張卡片，然後換左手邊玩家成為新的起始玩家開始選商品。</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgz0qpeDCvtiyvPQ7-eWkiZTy0NkxdPrS43AQZuIO1fQa3fEFTnwvFPc5QOfbTg6Ir0GGDb4YAdFTp0dM4aFbFW2yCJLkik8nA3ncVgLf-qA4HvR3-NHx3T31WZhvhYBk69RFvVsoUJIrfo9wQgL7MMx-K6Gzwhm_m8CA1Q3qjfuo-MvwtAOLkZP-OTwOk/s600/DSC04961.JPG\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲當這幾張有特殊符號的卡片被放進袋子後，會發動能力。由左而右分別是：讓左邊的玩家抽一張卡片、自己抽一張卡片、讓右邊的玩家抽一張卡片～不管是誰，抽到卡片之後就必須立刻放進自己的袋子中，如果抽到的卡片上也有特殊符號，那放進袋子之後就繼續執行新的特殊符號。（有可能會連續發動好多次）</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEi_efCHu7d0QRJ67c65gNSsLDB8VEucVQblUc3MKXDOwLIpQ7mPpJb92V9VUF_n1vcTEr_qHHObodHiAeiCEm4V246oV5kilHfv1w9ZNdrFfGqLIWF2zFLM-BxURk7OVcB8-r4TTB0w7PefcXtfjeEfMuqgHr5Jo1fiSVg6pwnGS7a_znK5ytdWTII2CN0/s4760/DSC04959.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEi_efCHu7d0QRJ67c65gNSsLDB8VEucVQblUc3MKXDOwLIpQ7mPpJb92V9VUF_n1vcTEr_qHHObodHiAeiCEm4V246oV5kilHfv1w9ZNdrFfGqLIWF2zFLM-BxURk7OVcB8-r4TTB0w7PefcXtfjeEfMuqgHr5Jo1fiSVg6pwnGS7a_znK5ytdWTII2CN0/s600/DSC04959.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲袋子的置放規則：拿到的商品卡必須放進袋子中，每個袋子必須符合其中一個條件才能放進去：１．袋內的商品都是同顏色，折扣％總和不能超過１００％　２．袋內的商品必須都是不同顏色且折扣％都要相同～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">有一個很特殊的規則是，只要你符合規定，隨時可以調整三個袋子內的商品位置～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">＊以上圖來說我左邊的袋子放了三雙鞋（橘色）３０＋２０＋５０，已經１００％滿了、上面的袋子放了三種顏色的４０％商品，還有兩種顏色有機會可以放（共五種顏色）、右邊的袋子放了兩種３０％的商品，結果這時候得到一張５０％的紫色商品．．．．沒地方可以去，因此就爆袋了！</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgpiqESP7mVhRJWGkqAFba6-tARUFQ0rxC73VGizFPiBoU4FpcrJL3XbiesidTxDfdqaeJanHEbszsb5dxK-Mr4zi58-2YhbQKo9Ln35QxPfLlpXY0albLmYwXF-wrc3qzK4FWfnn6vuMct_VW7cLhOyk8O_o81-Z0WX9dA9s0CPn4Om_lhsnFyrDtUGj4/s4492/DSC04960.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgpiqESP7mVhRJWGkqAFba6-tARUFQ0rxC73VGizFPiBoU4FpcrJL3XbiesidTxDfdqaeJanHEbszsb5dxK-Mr4zi58-2YhbQKo9Ln35QxPfLlpXY0albLmYwXF-wrc3qzK4FWfnn6vuMct_VW7cLhOyk8O_o81-Z0WX9dA9s0CPn4Om_lhsnFyrDtUGj4/s600/DSC04960.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲此外還有代購的任務卡，拿到的時候會放在角色卡的下方，每一輪最多只能拿兩張，如果拿了三張也會爆袋！</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">＊只要有任何一位玩家爆袋，這一輪遊戲就會立刻結束，爆袋的玩家必須選擇將某一袋內的商品全部丟棄。接著所有人就把這輪得到的商品與代購任務卡收起來，接著進行下一輪。三輪之後遊戲就結束了～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhLpCi_YqHlWy0bS57EAKYjQnxLyjtDojrpXyC9KKjDc4lupYF1TJVNrhFJiveLAhi1nvYSfBURo2rlI0-ops1bWLqNqzyBQU2MdFxYEgkBgPu2BvtAoPxGIcQjC-T3_eqo1fbgC6JwuErHEviR2KxJuzDjgZ8nRtVoO0cdaGcj6myOw2eAM3_lynOfYh8/s5048/DSC04962.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhLpCi_YqHlWy0bS57EAKYjQnxLyjtDojrpXyC9KKjDc4lupYF1TJVNrhFJiveLAhi1nvYSfBURo2rlI0-ops1bWLqNqzyBQU2MdFxYEgkBgPu2BvtAoPxGIcQjC-T3_eqo1fbgC6JwuErHEviR2KxJuzDjgZ8nRtVoO0cdaGcj6myOw2eAM3_lynOfYh8/s600/DSC04962.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲遊戲結束的計分很簡單，商品卡看數字計分，２０％的一張２分，３０％的一張３分．．．．代購卡則是看是否有達成，有的話一張得５分，沒達成的話一張扣３分～這邊要注意的是，一個商品只能拿去給一張代購卡使用，不能一卡多用喔～最後最高分的玩家獲勝，如果平手，最多商品卡的玩家獲勝！</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEj1SninCubuNL0hcrPTdHj4Hm-nXj4aFQ9SyXhIPw15Ml61Zjw2VHW65hk2_BS-VA3xSzSTzw7qMfT-H720oX18AaPECmDekZQ94TWbyyRjxvBilcbVi9DsEBdZZdzQJE75JpmXvcjhp9fcCYtkRklOEsx1eC6iktGv6wgiUGaTgRJbDgitfTLQoIv61hc/s600/DSC04954.JPG\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲這邊簡單翻譯一下人物的特殊能力，人物名稱其實都有對應的台語喔：</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">KIASEE（怕死 kiann-sí）：當你需要抽卡的時候，你可以指定讓另一位玩家抽卡</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Mr. KIASU（怕輸 kiaⁿ-su）：可以把所有的６０％都當作２０％看</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">AI SWEE（愛美 ài-suí）：可以把所有的鞋子（橘色）都視為任意顏色</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">YAU QWEE（餓鬼，愛吃鬼 gō-kuí）：拿到６０％的食物（綠色）時，直接放在角色卡上，不會佔用袋子空間</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">AH MA（阿嬤 a-má）：可以把所有的２０％都視為任意顏色</p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEiYbh5ZNhgL3QWxTiO9ZKf4jv95tgiXvjsaqGl30jCUqgwJyk5onnPX739IRgNXS69jmtVDTGwDWXaylhxyYz2shhCchboJrExzfnllNXFseSKo2uc14FU7HKZ3gx9uF0HoIQgkny2zOFODXOOC4lD2Wx7Fdlqg2SPdgwHqkSh97Sb61LhZFVTUuHq0aVI\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEiYbh5ZNhgL3QWxTiO9ZKf4jv95tgiXvjsaqGl30jCUqgwJyk5onnPX739IRgNXS69jmtVDTGwDWXaylhxyYz2shhCchboJrExzfnllNXFseSKo2uc14FU7HKZ3gx9uF0HoIQgkny2zOFODXOOC4lD2Wx7Fdlqg2SPdgwHqkSh97Sb61LhZFVTUuHq0aVI\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>叫你阿嬤來啊！！！</strong></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">我必須說，身為一款派對家庭桌遊，《Shop until you drop Lah! 瞎拼袋禍日》的主題選得很不錯，去大賣場蝦拼購物有誰會不愛～遊戲中如果還沒有太大的利害關係時，大家選卡片的目標甚至是這個商品我喜不喜歡，而不是這個商品對我有沒有利～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">遊戲的機制不只是簡單，而且還非常的直覺。不管是商品的價值（折扣越多的商品分數越高），或是爆袋的設定還有代購的任務都非常好懂，因此真的很適合闔家遊玩，這款遊戲我會推薦給：喜歡逛大賣場的媽媽、喜歡看百貨公司商品目錄的姊姊、喜歡各種３Ｃ產品的哥哥、喜歡吃各種美食的爸爸，當然，最重要的當然是．．．．你的阿嬤！把阿嬤們也拉進來玩吧！不要以為阿嬤會輸喔！</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiFxh39Vg4Teg9CtXUK7adhrePnRg84XDkuU9ynU_UGBmLAk5ylQqlFvhvS1SYa_LibHTDfTdjIGoQof_pqHmofgVdx36SCA6o3MRgf6HD-ma05yAV6uJa4TSSeiz5D8pe9oalsC9scgQpEXp6jo2dtMgOrtqfVwuCCsKtnmOnBkRmo3AeRSjqnMTvSTt8/s4784/DSC04963.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiFxh39Vg4Teg9CtXUK7adhrePnRg84XDkuU9ynU_UGBmLAk5ylQqlFvhvS1SYa_LibHTDfTdjIGoQof_pqHmofgVdx36SCA6o3MRgf6HD-ma05yAV6uJa4TSSeiz5D8pe9oalsC9scgQpEXp6jo2dtMgOrtqfVwuCCsKtnmOnBkRmo3AeRSjqnMTvSTt8/s600/DSC04963.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲遊戲收納照</p><p><br></p>', '2024-11-18 10:25:53', '2024-11-18 10:25:53', 1, 'forum-1731896753833-810113579.jpg');
INSERT INTO `forum_posts` (`id`, `user_id`, `title`, `content`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `status`, `cover_image`) VALUES
(17, 1, '【桌遊開箱報】Mission control Critical Orbit 控制中心 臨界危機 開箱+介紹', '<h3><br></h3><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhfwKVd_7mcdmLkMQO9LxE9uk0Ti87WXDK3PIh3nTuvNZteSBp4pUD8ltcd3ANuz_r9_8Slkde9o70WMDDzP7yy7652Jvg5I4RIK1oRLasvS0Z0uUg_-Wuozf-sGH93-bZur-afe5q2xJ8Rvo1zymGARow6pvHgdAPpuaF-YJBIn4nCtOsALbZvg1IfJr8/s3532/DSC04890.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhfwKVd_7mcdmLkMQO9LxE9uk0Ti87WXDK3PIh3nTuvNZteSBp4pUD8ltcd3ANuz_r9_8Slkde9o70WMDDzP7yy7652Jvg5I4RIK1oRLasvS0Z0uUg_-Wuozf-sGH93-bZur-afe5q2xJ8Rvo1zymGARow6pvHgdAPpuaF-YJBIn4nCtOsALbZvg1IfJr8/s600/DSC04890.JPG\"></a></p><p><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEi1aPPp9bJ1lJVyoFynDzkwTFgmbzwalLR7NOWCCIJNc94oonB5425qt-h3ayBDPAFXrzGQwDx643Oz6H8GtsFSGZ2bVE81MhzM7jEJIRPJ2od14D2M_Zr6-INuxMzpjq4nVVKqrG7Som1faRg9V2_nJaVKTLAG19TVKX0oMWUJI8MqH7fgMEWuyVSXTbM\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">合作遊戲，有玩過吧？骰寫遊戲，也有玩過吧？板拼遊戲，也有玩過對吧？不對稱能力遊戲，應該也有玩過吧？但四種合在一起呢？你有沒有玩過合作類型＋不對稱能力的骰寫板拼遊戲呢！？很難想像對吧，沒錯，我還沒玩之前也很難想像會是怎樣的狀況，但實際玩過之後，這款遊戲一週之內我居然連開了七場！？至於到底在玩什麼，今天就來介紹給大家聽～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><em>墨丘利三號太空船從地球出發之後順利土星，但一連串的意外，使得之後的既定行程無法繼續。因此在艦長果斷的決策之下，他們順利返回大氣層外側的軌道。但就在這個時候，發現氧氣供應管路出了狀況，如果不趕快維修，很可能會功虧一簣，就這樣魂斷家門之前～因此地球上的ＳＡＧＡ成員：美國、德國與印度，一起來幫忙進行最終的修復～</em></p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEj-XYIv3kJn33d5J8DcqO7t5ugh1CgZvfoFqenPf-7dkWiNDG8k8z9s5O7g7YbfLHt67nVFSz7T2QUkwBO2BKM420AUnajlaxAl1DPPx1y3CZs0THGPLKXmB6PtX2UHZdWy2ZlV6qZEPfAKhJWKFf7hl3C-T81_nZhOJTcHIjyQq1jhgVp_l494SayY178\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhfwKVd_7mcdmLkMQO9LxE9uk0Ti87WXDK3PIh3nTuvNZteSBp4pUD8ltcd3ANuz_r9_8Slkde9o70WMDDzP7yy7652Jvg5I4RIK1oRLasvS0Z0uUg_-Wuozf-sGH93-bZur-afe5q2xJ8Rvo1zymGARow6pvHgdAPpuaF-YJBIn4nC