 class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgcLvWvKWvHm3dvaMwByK5K8eJnOCu1sbp_JHzylTeIsa5nHhnd4QDDtHli6f9QRy62Qm3ugU_RmCcFhdu8YM10hMRQzoFg850b0hIYC01eYFsnfZZNOY2gszXAMM15X4xAHw1t8jFHeVMpIx95Kfhb0MUXRFHgy6HK7MvT-ubdcF0mHmcp8F3oJzxo8t4/s5260/DSC04900.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgcLvWvKWvHm3dvaMwByK5K8eJnOCu1sbp_JHzylTeIsa5nHhnd4QDDtHli6f9QRy62Qm3ugU_RmCcFhdu8YM10hMRQzoFg850b0hIYC01eYFsnfZZNOY2gszXAMM15X4xAHw1t8jFHeVMpIx95Kfhb0MUXRFHgy6HK7MvT-ubdcF0mHmcp8F3oJzxo8t4/s600/DSC04900.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲圖板有凹槽，這很重要，因為到時候這位太空人會非常的忙！！！！！</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhvd7DnYOLttW1mFK-NVr7ovkp64aY74KQUV5hxUNpewungV5yIv2uAmQKdO6LzdY8ez_nG7c5GDPdP8zhVV8riCn_WvNd8hMHK3yaoH0-CHgyGWN-xh5A0vMOspESGZpVXk_fGcYCHaf3ueff-RmE-TsDEXNq9PnAX4h018lOrCTdZ6ZaeAujbTLo63Fg/s5116/DSC04901.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhvd7DnYOLttW1mFK-NVr7ovkp64aY74KQUV5hxUNpewungV5yIv2uAmQKdO6LzdY8ez_nG7c5GDPdP8zhVV8riCn_WvNd8hMHK3yaoH0-CHgyGWN-xh5A0vMOspESGZpVXk_fGcYCHaf3ueff-RmE-TsDEXNq9PnAX4h018lOrCTdZ6ZaeAujbTLo63Fg/s600/DSC04901.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲３顆科技感的六面骰</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiJoGdM0MOdLX7knO87alTdTcVsA8VMbDd-iZujtfkCQ1f4tw3TWruONWjBqUY2qLcpUC-YTaVEpZaEYUgvupKaSYesWwS5FADhKGOQqHoVOSofpFTRysZfAiqZykpa8shvYFJ6W8j9gmOFU5GrHr-0ZNau7ZZGa1rdpG8CrkvzG0xF5LXVTqu-m6KJhAo/s4636/DSC04902.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiJoGdM0MOdLX7knO87alTdTcVsA8VMbDd-iZujtfkCQ1f4tw3TWruONWjBqUY2qLcpUC-YTaVEpZaEYUgvupKaSYesWwS5FADhKGOQqHoVOSofpFTRysZfAiqZykpa8shvYFJ6W8j9gmOFU5Gr