</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEg_-uidWuIL7Z9nW8VMq0yYbHi6VZGnB5_WpbBg6dkJDGEotehqWYMFbh3XuaZNY143FEt1nNs6U9sCVFNw9scms4VLiOFn-l7Buzc8usVPsG7w_bCldkj8mBLOMQJnogxDPyscn1TqvY5nqgxdsz0TUZY6OO2jeF_9PLGMuNW6B4_qbISQnLARoVFk4Yk/s3388/DSC04303.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEg_-uidWuIL7Z9nW8VMq0yYbHi6VZGnB5_WpbBg6dkJDGEotehqWYMFbh3XuaZNY143FEt1nNs6U9sCVFNw9scms4VLiOFn-l7Buzc8usVPsG7w_bCldkj8mBLOMQJnogxDPyscn1TqvY5nqgxdsz0TUZY6OO2jeF_9PLGMuNW6B4_qbISQnLARoVFk4Yk/s600/DSC04303.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲擺出來的雪季版河流擴充</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgjuh3Ne6uvteJFKRaM7Urywi_oibbZ0byTxgD3uH1AtizPWhrunMe-Gj-awVMvDho1l7Of2bgxdcQeJ6cMwNYhoIeGpOrxbR_XA1JTH8sUzc_doZXZWTRyI217r50lyZFEnnalfkRPn_zEgVtjKWUXFA-AT5X6E8QzgiYO_NyadWPO1ZQsZfvftVnukHg/w640-h640/632c39bd769f0c68e7ce8baa_Carc_Winter_Play2.jpg\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲這張是天鵝的官方圖，我也有拍類似的，但覺得這個背景很美～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">（可以看到新板塊上有很多可愛的小動物）</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgeOh1wElYElsCnSrZ1xjwXvLrVFpbgtV-gIjWHPMCfUHGkrDAPdwKnSZG53myuBNNRPlJbMInSXsGdqx44z3IyhLvjnHqqLywzaClQSv5HMoc4IzgTtnLIq6T0MJBrp4PtAZ5kZw9xuFgEUMeMWL-Rj8Oaa-hPTH8n1PX3_KfgtvZqpsvylVyvR0b4nek/s4620/DSC04304.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgeOh1wElYElsCnSrZ1xjwXvLrVFpbgtV-gIjWHPMCfUHGkrDAPdwKnSZG53myuBNNRPlJbMInSXsGdqx44z3IyhLvjnHqqLywzaClQSv5HMoc4IzgTtnLIq6T0MJBrp4PtAZ5kZw9xuFgEUMeMWL-Rj8Oaa-hPTH8n1PX3_KfgtvZqpsvylVyvR0b4nek/s600/DSC04304.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲米寶就．．．米寶</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEj3A91k-JZqW_iOxFQkshRFp7eDe5xDjd5ZQ7S6ZZM1yKPkHaVpT8SjzywHH4n7BAVz2jwdSLdJdWh2TYZS-DTssXGGGNAbIqKUP1SfhefF_hKIXMeA-WGk5miT2WC_aQI3YFeC5WqokCTMsL2i7Orga7o0p8AaV-uEXImYWad3jb6hp_mnOiL5WH86xCs/s3532/DSC04306.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEj3A91k-JZqW_iOxFQkshRFp7eDe5xDjd5ZQ7S6ZZM1yKPkHaVpT8SjzywHH4n7BAVz2jwdSLdJdWh2TYZS-DTssXGGGNAbIqKUP1SfhefF_hKIXMeA-WGk5miT2WC_aQI3YFeC5WqokCTMsL2i7Orga7o0p8AaV-uEXImYWad3jb6hp_mnOiL5WH86xCs/s600/DSC04306.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲這次也有加入修道院長這個擴充～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">（但其實規則跟基本版的修道院長規則也一樣）</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEiazUhG8fQIpKl0Cacf02VaEKg08WL-wl3I97YkivVhXBaxj6dVzcCYUUciYfXersIPskThXITVFoslQV7qEllYF3iW9RTEoKFzVJSdSC8Dfd0mpsoaBBLfIy_DxFTMr_B-znHw6BROdpNYyBZ__z1diccvR7Q4nqnUdGPWA3bqUuFSyANTgPWa26yG0uQ\"></p><p><br></p><p><strong>雪～一片一片一片～</strong></p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">這邊先公布答案，其實我想點的歌曲就是范曉萱的《雪人》，上面這句歌詞跟這款遊戲真的很搭～《卡卡頌 雪季版》就像是一款被艾莎施放了冰雪魔法的《卡卡頌》，從原本的綠意盎然變成了美麗的冰雪大地～雖然說原本的《卡卡頌》已經很漂亮了，但《卡卡頌 雪季版》的美麗又更上了一層樓～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">本作最大的缺點是，在規則上《卡卡頌 雪季版》跟原本的《卡卡頌》沒什麼不同，因此可能會有不少人覺得《卡卡頌 雪季版》有點占櫃子～但對於沒有《卡卡頌》的人來說，這一款真的是可以無腦收～加上聽說《卡卡頌 雪季版》是限定版，限量是殘酷的！這個道理，我想大家應該都懂～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">以上便是這次簡單的介紹，希望這款美麗的遊戲沒有被我拍醜了～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhhsS_BodKFZLszC90yPTtMY2kgNArZ0MIoE_fPF_wBj39NXLoJRHO4LeHr1ecQEbBwSTlmKZvGvsSBCbQgMe68UbhkvKR-Y7lXSVBpGikyS8iVMoYGYqWsN6POHBom09FMyvCB0nlg96sfz1PyDCZqbaGx0yVioaw43wEW73_XtQfyHphnntjg1pW1vLs/s5048/DSC04307.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhhsS_BodKFZLszC90yPTtMY2kgNArZ0MIoE_fPF_wBj39NXLoJRHO4LeHr1ecQEbBwSTlmKZvGvsSBCbQgMe68UbhkvKR-Y7lXSVBpGikyS8iVMoYGYqWsN6POHBom09FMyvCB0nlg96sfz1PyDCZqbaGx0yVioaw43wEW73_XtQfyHphnntjg1pW1vLs/s600/DSC04307.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲遊戲收納照</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjvHZY_5ae3gECJO1brC-yElN27JINbWWCTjubWlZEmWhq8IZ3hdDhyphenhyphenGHtjAB2-adVB_R3i7h7ykT1gzqPud_yH_4IBxV8L01l-69ygp59ZGLiq_B6PGN_-K2BLLQrYzQ8sBXWjCCq12jNxNyozA-gVxwtXNqGxX8xCuFGUhYSdLYppNv0oe1RBh18hmGo/w640-h640/632c39bb4e318b8b1b121232_Carc_Winter_Play1.jpg\"></p><p><br></p>', '2024-11-18 10:37:44', '2024-11-18 10:37:44', 1, 'forum-1731897464046-732466719.jpg');
INSERT INTO `forum_posts` (`id`, `user_id`, `title`, `content`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `status`, `cover_image`) VALUES
(26, 1, '【桌遊開箱報】Pawlitics : Candidogs vs Politicats 選汪與喵 開箱+介紹', '<h3><strong>【桌遊開箱報】Pawlitics : Candidogs vs Politicats 選汪與喵 開箱+介紹</strong></h3><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhWlUf9XXIJmnfh1BzopFGpqFlr2w5N6pDD9iRc3xoG7vspzL6-IgyGGGPQ_YdnAtmWq05oshPgXnAPSr49PYjrcJbNyvHST7kAIsYYUZOL5qXslOq2v1-y7sFjeeAlDmNI7pgeZetLksemGkJZ3cNpATmL6WZDpSdkO6W4RBaSYTgNKXdRIGUtlnr6J2U/s2840/DSC04201.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhWlUf9XXIJmnfh1BzopFGpqFlr2w5N6pDD9iRc3xoG7vspzL6-IgyGGGPQ_YdnAtmWq05oshPgXnAPSr49PYjrcJbNyvHST7kAIsYYUZOL5qXslOq2v1-y7sFjeeAlDmNI7pgeZetLksemGkJZ3cNpATmL6WZDpSdkO6W4RBaSYTgNKXdRIGUtlnr6J2U/s600/DSC04201.JPG\"></a></p><p><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEgZeDgIghkA9z8B4IotNGfZTtT4MpzccsPH9IYcb5d1Fq_Yx_jpG1p0bTqKWIKYByV1DmB4OlI0hptmzsdelqYIno-8aDXcv1MP39exhmnNWz4C-Yb2NwQhdGLookCB_ARjNk7PooJi9VYFjZx1052T3Yc-ej9uzVtjaZY6LH25FCE1MoDW0bcGEdCt=w320-h136\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">如果真要說台灣人有什麼過人之處的話，那大概就是『選舉』的能力，還有對『選舉』這件事情的熱衷程度～因為我們不像美國有各種專屬於自己城市的球隊可以支持～可以對著敵隊的其他城市球迷亂吼，謾罵～似乎就是因為少了這個情感宣洩的管道，因此每次遇到『選舉』大家就好像過動兒一樣，一股腦的把各種熱情都投注在裡面了～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">這次這款披著可愛外皮的《選汪與喵》，骨子裡就是一款實實在在的選舉遊戲，搭配即將到來的總統選舉來玩，應該會特別的對味～</p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEgYU4HxY-Ij1lmyOq2eAeZykiHU9O76An9b_STPOjxOL_cHs0L2-3Ilt3oy2RNRTePJhm19WBjjLTb3BUkM1Twr6LTLkOY_4PlB77NOywNMd8pGAFlu-E_QMWZAWTiZkNi_VViuJ9bLTsrgj5EEmb75amn2pE7rpeCmJ87J9gSGTly1jnYSFlSPqyxz=w320-h136\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhWlUf9XXIJmnfh1BzopFGpqFlr2w5N6pDD9iRc3xoG7vspzL6-IgyGGGPQ_YdnAtmWq05oshPgXnAPSr49PYjrcJbNyvHST7kAIsYYUZOL5qXslOq2v1-y7sFjeeAlDmNI7pgeZetLksemGkJZ3cNpATmL6WZDpSdkO6W4RBaSYTgNKXdRIGUtlnr6J2U/s2840/DSC04201.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhWlUf9XXIJmnfh1BzopFGpqFlr2w5N6pDD9iRc3xoG7vspzL6-IgyGGGPQ_YdnAtmWq05oshPgXnAPSr49PYjrcJbNyvHST7kAIsYYUZOL5qXslOq2v1-y7sFjeeAlDmNI7pgeZetLksemGkJZ3cNpATmL6WZDpSdkO6W4RBaSYTgNKXdRIGUtlnr6J2U/s600/DSC04201.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲封面可以看到很可愛的動物們～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">（但似乎有不少人不太能接受兔兔有人類的牙齒）</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgwBVsV0oT0p1HLuU84KZ5G_MmcvBEqyvOO-AsES0QBmjamPkmuZ17iEXaIhu4M8RKO6Bz0aV2tmS4WngENM-yWBTQVcACVFmpDCw3wizmN6qANbIwob9kyf-yuSYYdUa8NKwMvIzSPxrSCHdpSQdGVPoo3G_vwlcUplBCq7GQ879_hJFhC-cJ9uRT-qsM/s4056/DSC04202.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgwBVsV0oT0p1HLuU84KZ5G_MmcvBEqyvOO-AsES0QBmjamPkmuZ17iEXaIhu4M8RKO6Bz0aV2tmS4WngENM-yWBTQVcACVFmpDCw3wizmN6qANbIwob9kyf-yuSYYdUa8NKwMvIzSPxrSCHdpSQdGVPoo3G_vwlcUplBCq7GQ879_hJFhC-cJ9uRT-qsM/s600/DSC04202.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲遊戲人數：3-5人　建議年齡：10+　遊戲時間：30-45mins</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgHgaKATPzeJFxA7W7eF79A1uiggi-w28p6kDHqBSIYfdi-C00EHTH_kaQyfITXkW0pHejMpGMtHBgRtErME16dtGdiGsg20YMhESk_krr2lvdyr-lGdpoxajrufJ62bB9n5BC6eWk8T8JB8QKCA8fosSbvnbkAR7AAxz_1RVLKsWo7BLzRM43A-p5GGhM/s3104/DSC04203.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgHgaKATPzeJFxA7W7eF79A1uiggi-w28p6kDHqBSIYfdi-C00EHTH_kaQyfITXkW0pHejMpGMtHBgRtErME16dtGdiGsg20YMhESk_krr2lvdyr-lGdpoxajrufJ62bB9n5BC6eWk8T8JB8QKCA8fosSbvnbkAR7AAxz_1RVLKsWo7BLzRM43A-p5GGhM/s600/DSC04203.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲這場詭譎多變的選舉，你想要投給誰呢！？</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">（不是阿！你一次蓋兩個人，這張已經廢票了吧！）</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh4TXbpgxwreonKG7zCYgkevT5FUhuBe7iG3vPGlab47X