dIcZeczq9A8EBuSHRC83RmvfwVPqwxBCFt9HLXFhXrA3yztKj61exjjly_rtLAN0mBXGC9Bz0atJm85PjMvZXUbzScPb4LyVT-iZhs1bhQyNQ0ZfZcvaBxNp9GnJn74oVdvsnWfJMdzByTYqSNM_wsTYllHZnJbmYUdfQrUmFmdNHu8JRLfM/s600/DSC04212.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲玩家幫助卡可以讓大家快速看懂所有的圖示</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiqcDNHqPGOhDGy91JGwKyXCSIcZ1dbYz3ekzYEdV3Np-e7rRTXqyj-6J5f5614gKEHPCMkIM164OK0Zayz7mEKtHMgWmKMPY3FehXZLyhNp0xas2fO5MfQqeDKu5ujt2hlCLjnzPtkQZQ368esoV3W4e4KmDgH8dGHwIj6WzTogLQs4XMYP6OJxKNeOR0/s3148/DSC04213.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiqcDNHqPGOhDGy91JGwKyXCSIcZ1dbYz3ekzYEdV3Np-e7rRTXqyj-6J5f5614gKEHPCMkIM164OK0Zayz7mEKtHMgWmKMPY3FehXZLyhNp0xas2fO5MfQqeDKu5ujt2hlCLjnzPtkQZQ368esoV3W4e4KmDgH8dGHwIj6WzTogLQs4XMYP6OJxKNeOR0/s600/DSC04213.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲目標卡，遊戲中進行兩次選舉，如果有達成，結束時會獲得分數～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgDLf-pXnHGBZuzvYCoJkD0SGrcb7En7Yn6qz5nXnZYEhabm0DhSQkXyDqs0y-8SMhuyVccRAXyBptjuw0R291H_jGWgmv7x7Z8yj0291Vl_H5kbdomXs7QQhadkSgGY-JFjwP4vUGQ3EJgQRTI4qdNg57qvl7D-ZaxHa8BZcZoJB_wzmOQlHAHAG5L1Z8/s4024/DSC04214.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgDLf-pXnHGBZuzvYCoJkD0SGrcb7En7Yn6qz5nXnZYEhabm0DhSQkXyDqs0y-8SMhuyVccRAXyBptjuw0R291H_jGWgmv7x7Z8yj0291Vl_H5kbdomXs7QQhadkSgGY-JFjwP4vUGQ3EJgQRTI4qdNg57qvl7D-ZaxHa8BZcZoJB_wzmOQlHAHAG5L1Z8/s600/DSC04214.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲媒體卡，可以用來帶各種風向</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEg1MHh7piUwT47UAQG2ffcrl011DbU8cGqaj34NxZF6-gCKngSLJRUDDITD7RGA4rtUH_gmi-pSUYbVzoHhZE41ndk_c42R7d_uvTK-yP6pHhyOzjDBbIggLH37W87WyQmwcWutQf9XcZrc8jDN-egv9O9fqyJ1jixOFhyphenhyphenUg3AZ6a87BW4fl9P2NWH1Mjk/s4860/DSC04215.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEg1MHh7piUwT47UAQG2ffcrl011DbU8cGqaj34NxZF6-gCKngSLJRUDDITD7RGA4rtUH_gmi-pSUYbVzoHhZE41ndk_c42R7d_uvTK-yP6pHhyOzjDBbIggLH37W87WyQmwcWutQf9XcZrc8jDN-egv9O9fqyJ1jixOFhyphenhyphenUg3AZ6a87BW4fl9P2NWH1Mjk/s600/DSC04215.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲三個陣營的候選人們</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhIx5qi5SQd8HCWayL_qov8DLDUtgmXhVFn8wbu-4u5gQ55Wmmx_nV_W0uGmvWWERleOotsFUzdiKyH7z42tIscOB3q9oE-NHv2944yALoRR8p12zXLFfwEH11YZmQ1YJQokPxkUquGi0p21vTr_BeUjSeEgk_GcuXFQEoQxcKwKCsTBV5bWN2ZelGak-k/s4340/DSC04216.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhIx5qi5SQd8HCWayL_qov8DLDUtgmXhVFn8wbu-4u5gQ55Wmmx_nV_W0uGmvWWERleOotsFUzdiKyH7z42tIscOB3q9oE-NHv2944yALoRR8p12zXLFfwEH11YZmQ1YJQokPxkUquGi0p21vTr_BeUjSeEgk_GcuXFQEoQxcKwKCsTBV5bWN2ZelGak-k/s600/DSC04216.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲貓派、狗派與兔派的手牌～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEjeQ5l7zhnehKqTVQrvS72sbC9q5LydEZBbyd4Bfpdg7XbpwYvzM6_2vCu-C54OZPMWwRkkhD1Z9h_IL3Ev7uZ2YlNqHBFASwHK-DdaTnSrdw-mkt93TCWfBF4CKwCyAjWfXJWo7ewJPiBL7MZ74WoD8LpuCWpR2KLXgivPoU8VaUZFqpQGWqxhk8uYdsY\"></p><p><br></p><p>規則其實不難，我這邊就偷懶用官方的圖片來做簡單的說明～</p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiGKI2n59CZNnm34cB1OWzqlJ8BPEoGu8DzIGNf5Go_DBL7TpxYi3l9xchY6YNIeCw82YNU7yaAVEa4rZVxun0VDKvrJJ9QNp_1w7cXpwylTL9UZiEtPRu9nQHPXOZo_6WmacE_SVrsh27ye4XPGoFt_JUsaF0sdDzowsf3cK7l329vQpzYNgaCQ31NFBQ/s960/01.png\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiGKI2n59CZNnm34cB1OWzqlJ8BPEoGu8DzIGNf5Go_DBL7TpxYi3l9xchY6YNIeCw82YNU7yaAVEa4rZVxun0VDKvrJJ9QNp_1w7cXpwylTL9UZiEtPRu9nQHPXOZo_6WmacE_SVrsh27ye4XPGoFt_JUsaF0sdDzowsf3cK7l329vQpzYNgaCQ31NFBQ/w640-h640/01.png\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲每次輪到你的時候會先進行棄Ｎ然後捕到４張，接著進行造勢行動，從手牌打出１張卡片並執行效果（打出的這張卡片同時也是你當前的玩家角色）～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiGSooim75YcarX7jdDgUcuwv0EucnAqQ2on4D_qinaUaSmCw9Y-KTF7FMVl7rtefS38WLsuwSj-BRWUgiLbYMKs4GqHAq-9ZXMxLpy6BWBX-6rwesdvUa0hxePmBxzTxdnQ-Pq2B5PiG_TjR2hQkbBoYXUbf3GZbbsUKtX6R7J3uoz4XfGbWKAVe1rbOo/s960/02.png\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiGSooim75YcarX7jdDgUcuwv0EucnAqQ2on4D_qinaUaSmCw9Y-KTF7FMVl7rtefS38WLsuwSj-BRWUgiLbYMKs4GqHAq-9ZXMxLpy6BWBX-6rwesdvUa0hxePmBxzTxdnQ-Pq2B5PiG_TjR2hQkbBoYXUbf3GZbbsUKtX6R7J3uoz4XfGbWKAVe1rbOo/w640-h640/02.png\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲接下來是共同階段，所有當前角色是『樁腳』的玩家都會從國庫拿到１個罐罐～然後大家如果有符合條件的媒體卡，也可以打出並執行效果～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">＊打出的媒體卡執行之後，會面朝下放在自己面前～等等投票階段會根據媒體牌的數量決定你可以投的張數～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh-N-Z5Ig7WuFBMcJQsKGc_W2uRLfGly5e76UHJarIB0OwtjmaO1sApAgpp_-62L693iEjYz8r4j1wCRKHxDJxO8TR7LabUILJXd3kNz4H-w-0womVRNezKXFPergnwa83l1aC0hdu9FTO0YMS3guvIDfVIpWh8PwXAr2O7L-LScl35UsmJCtuOBrASRMs/s1024/03.jpeg\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh-N-Z5Ig7WuFBMcJQsKGc_W2uRLfGly5e76UHJarIB0OwtjmaO1sApAgpp_-62L693iEjYz8r4j1wCRKHxDJxO8TR7LabUILJXd3kNz4H-w-0womVRNezKXFPergnwa83l1aC0hdu9FTO0YMS3guvIDfVIpWh8PwXAr2O7L-LScl35UsmJCtuOBrASRMs/w640-h640/03.jpeg\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲出事了！阿伯！累積發生３次大事件就會進入投票階段～遊戲中的大事件有以下四種：</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">１．國庫被塞爆（國庫太肥所以民眾暴動？）２．國庫被掏空（這個大家暴動應該很好懂）３．風向到達狗狗極端４．風向到達貓貓極端（風向太偏會物極必反！？）５．任一牌堆被抽光</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">把國庫掏空，或是風向到達兩種極端都會讓引發的人扣分～因此樁腳階段可以從國庫領罐罐也不要太高興～如果領到國庫被掏空，可是會被扣分的～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhbkNETuioiyvvpqWhtSinhwLuEI63pqo1OwC6lEhtAS8g4RyhqPv7k-yTGNj-ITW4t_IKqltv6gg0t6Gp9Bb5woBWiA7pqDBjEIhIMnJTxYHW24Ivs6fmBmNc2woGV0ajCrHBTjpAJObLEu9eIMB0qeWQ8svG_xZu01gzzQM4VgGsPTcjNqi-RSbkSy90/s1024/04.jpeg\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhbkNETuioiyvvpqWhtSinhwLuEI63pqo1OwC6lEhtAS8g4RyhqPv7k-yTGNj-ITW4t_IKqltv6gg0t6Gp9Bb5woBWiA7pqDBjEIhIMnJTxYHW24Ivs6fmBmNc2woGV0ajCrHBTjpAJObLEu9eIMB0qeWQ8svG_xZu01gzzQM4VgGsPTcjNqi-RSbkSy90/w640-h640/04.jpeg\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲選舉階段很好懂，就是大家從手中打牌來決定是誰當選～比較特別的是，如果剛剛在遊戲中有打出媒體卡的玩家，每打出１張，就可以多投１票！果然，掌握媒體的人，就可以掌握政治啊～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">投票結束之後，會根據當選的候選人政見來分贓罐罐～接著進行下一輪的遊戲～兩次投票之後，遊戲結束，由最多分數（罐罐）的玩家獲勝！</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEgwaHMhRr9BEqbne_uL3byr_6h4d_dPvZgKDQAnMHJfsUc2rnO9pjp_gz5UJdMxXKGvi4ER0b2bI1a-b9EMerP0hAJuJrkMoMQ7ZbtdJY0o_-AEIxjQLt3EZyHqyW61dwO4zM3bPSBbCCDBAEm2xDfz2ui8QkWpzbihDhqJyETPru_qQ7oBoCs7qcuTbTk\"></p><p><br></p><p><strong>給我罐罐！其餘免談！</strong></p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">這遊戲最大的缺點就是太真實了！雖然遊戲一開始有發給你目標卡，讓你會想要去支持特定陣營，但如果發現大選將至，你支持的陣營好像．．．不太可能選上的時候，這時候真的就要『塊陶』啊！見風轉舵不過只是剛好，拿到罐罐才是真理～畢竟，要有投票給當選的人，才能一起分到一杯羹～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">帶風向這件事也相當有趣～大家都想要把風向帶得剛剛好，讓風向停留在崩潰邊緣的玩家可以獲得分數獎勵～但一個不小心讓風向爆炸，除了會加速投票的到來，也會讓該玩家扣分～快要投票前的風向掌控，也會有助於你想支持的候選人當選～也就是，風向帶得好，投票沒煩惱，罐罐自然不會少～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">遊戲的另外一大亮點是美術跟配件～動物們都很可愛～但也有一些朋友反映不太能接受兔兔的嘴巴有人類的牙齒～這點我想就是見仁見智了～但絕對不能忽視的是超級可愛的罐罐！！！！！當初我在桌遊展第一次看到的時候，我想說這應該是超級豪華版才會有的配件，真的沒想到居然是標配！每一盒都有！太猛了這個！怪不得菜鳥訪談的時候，設計師官官說他最滿意的就是這個罐罐！真的是誠意十足，帶入感也滿分！</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">希望這次的文章有讓大家更了解這款遊戲～趁著這次選舉的熱度，也希望《選汪與喵》可以『逆轟高飛！』在挖貝上取得好成績！最後當然是雙手奉上<a href=\"https://wabay.tw/projects/pawlitics?context=referral_from_marketing&amp;locale=zh-TW&amp;ref=6df725469b\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">挖貝的網址</a>啦～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NLwHtPTsQPg\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">菜鳥的設計師訪談影片</a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=79jEl9SYRFQ\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">逸馬的桌遊教學與實玩</a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgM6M_rcF81Qb5pXMUDIUP5OXRoShQorgVpCwVR_oOioqirwtsgA3yvyFAxlazboC65j35keCEQf0qHivLCgLxNED6TzhtLq6TH72E68KBlLhN0bRaIOCsFZek2COkUhS1IrDL_6v0XCnk_R8H7yPr9QX3fD5iYOXqAY7rdZT4C3-iC1j_N09ucI2lLaKM/s4800/DSC04217.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgM6M_rcF81Qb5pXMUDIUP5OXRoShQorgVpCwVR_oOioqirwtsgA3yvyFAxlazboC65j35keCEQf0qHivLCgLxNED6TzhtLq6TH72E68KBlLhN0bRaIOCsFZek2COkUhS1IrDL_6v0XCnk_R8H7yPr9QX3fD5iYOXqAY7rdZT4C3-iC1j_N09ucI2lLaKM/s600/DSC04217.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲遊戲收納照</p><h3><br></h3><p><br></p>', '2024-11-18 10:38:43', '2024-11-18 10:38:43', 1, 'forum-1731897523075-192515681.jpg'),
(27, 1, '【桌遊開箱報】臆斷推理殺人事件：福澤家的落日 開箱+介紹', '<h3><br></h3><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEheik9LoRNYEIzRwm_iqFxSV8QpuvCr8W0VJONuK8BW8b3VZiZDxFB4xzSJTljs7OyVDzjAEdF85dsY-1HTIwWWVqqcKkCRXdHC1LPZUIXwIQMpxxxYlRbey2cjq4XsiulcEm-OO6ia7V4ximHRJYukkJbWQxME37lgo63GB59GdJjcHuWAq4_qM3AHnbw/s3036/DSC04333.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEheik9LoRNYEIzRwm_iqFxSV8QpuvCr8W0VJONuK8BW8b3VZiZDxFB4xzSJTljs7OyVDzjAEdF85dsY-1HTIwWWVqqcKkCRXdHC1LPZUIXwIQMpxxxYlRbey2cjq4XsiulcEm-OO6ia7V4ximHRJYukkJbWQxME37lgo63GB59GdJjcHuWAq4_qM3AHnbw/s600/DSC04333.JPG\"></a></p><p><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEiPZh8n5sKrf6YClhqCbVdG6Apqromm-TWVWHJc2mi07rfW272Xhv4c01hy35JJf6Tlj9Y2kXE3lac6UTxMCPLeelReGIluZxdy_wZWwLGJzrg0Zg5UR6EXge02EFPoEoivGbVVTwIFGUeRNMQwz1UlCjcIysMBYe-SPQO3NV0t-jwIL3SA3c4YsAf91Wo\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">這遊戲在五年前，也就是２０１８年的時候，我們偉大的【桌遊推坑事件簿】居然有寫這款遊戲日文版的開箱介紹文！！！聽說這次美麗島桌遊節他也有出現，只可惜我沒有遇到他～推坑大～如果你有看到這篇，我們再找時間來玩桌遊吧～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">＊有沒有人跟我一樣，覺得福澤家的爺爺長得很像變老的兩津勘吉的？</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEgYU4HxY-Ij1lmyOq2eAeZykiHU9O76An9b_STPOjxOL_cHs0L2-3Ilt3oy2RNRTePJhm19WBjjLTb3BUkM1Twr6LTLkOY_4PlB77NOywNMd8pGAFlu-E_QMWZAWTiZkNi_VViuJ9bLTsrgj5EEmb75amn2pE7rpeCmJ87J9gSGTly1jnYSFlSPqyxz=w320-h136\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEheik9LoRNYEIzRwm_iqFxSV8QpuvCr8W0VJONuK8BW8b3VZiZDxFB4xzSJTljs7OyVDzjAEdF85dsY-1HTIwWWVqqcKkCRXdHC1LPZUIXwIQMpxxxYlRbey2cjq4XsiulcEm-OO6ia7V4ximHRJYukkJbWQxME37lgo63GB59GdJjcHuWAq4_qM3AHnbw/s3036/DSC04333.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEheik9LoRNYEIzRwm_iqFxSV8QpuvCr8W0VJONuK8BW8b3VZiZDxFB4xzSJTljs7OyVDzjAEdF85dsY-1HTIwWWVqqcKkCRXdHC1LPZUIXwIQMpxxxYlRbey2cjq4XsiulcEm-OO6ia7V4ximHRJYukkJbWQxME37lgo63GB59GdJjcHuWAq4_qM3AHnbw/s600/DSC04333.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲封面走舊舊的日系風格，另外不得不稱讚一下這個封面，裡面的每一個人物都跟遊戲中卡片上的動作與姿勢有些微的不同，整張完全是重畫的，相當的用心～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEj5v_7aJxW8iOalO2tlTqKcFJMXhFeZlVogn_aoVRQFwC7h2ShoC6QjCtAFxy4Umf-k6UAoTl6u9NyQCmiK-Lhh8O8mJT-q7hFSsD1VhZZ2Xn3G2UdFB5402Tg_SOBW_FhRtYP3qUBN5edTWoKZqzfvnqntAeMPjxAre_x1LJ8BQztBaLhjDkv-MMMRDXE/s4976/DSC04334.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEj5v_7aJxW8iOalO2tlTqKcFJMXhFeZlVogn_aoVRQFwC7h2ShoC6QjCtAFxy4Umf-k6UAoTl6u9NyQCmiK-Lhh8O8mJT-q7hFSsD1VhZZ2Xn3G2UdFB5402Tg_SOBW_FhRtYP3qUBN5edTWoKZqzfvnqntAeMPjxAre_x1LJ8BQztBaLhjDkv-MMMRDXE/s600/DSC04334.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲遊戲人數：3-6人　建議年齡：12+　遊戲時間：10-20mins</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEg5t6I1jRt0CH6QHQjtE8AUiTNT8N6CsBN4neT9kjvQNFWIMqEsUuE6Iw1rvA9WvrQwVahMO3hwdFqGPV6NzHZnxPSxnC0dXf-OkHJ737bkdvtkHtrrn1gENhcGMk54oAnlnr6Me03p99QdvXZQFo6by3Qa-hmekCStRHBIVH9a_gOu9n8jmst6r2Qt2b4/s2832/DSC04335.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEg5t6I1jRt0CH6QHQjtE8AUiTNT8N6CsBN4neT9kjvQNFWIMqEsUuE6Iw1rvA9WvrQwVahMO3hwdFqGPV6NzHZnxPSxnC0dXf-OkHJ737bkdvtkHtrrn1gENhcGMk54oAnlnr6Me03p99QdvXZQFo6by3Qa-hmekCStRHBIVH9a_gOu9n8jmst6r2Qt2b4/s600/DSC04335.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲盒底可以看到遊戲的故事背景，由於福澤家的家族密會中發生了凶殺案，因此找來了偵探們要抓出兇手，但大家不知道的是．．．凶殺案才剛剛開始．．．．</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEidG8TOxlE8LVcPNoh3oD6UU9X_f0_uh2IMi4HkV0nNWtTPwZUAPx-Lkyyzu2mGA3gXhlDQwIIpq0OOqfwN6bJssppKeFUTOXsyn7mJrh7F10W6YO8HWtvSqup4mwreCvZBz303Y6T7Y4L4d8pUFkvBqoc7apsE22RGycTBdQU1p6a3Z8LyuUHEe5emhyY/s4194/DSC04336.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEidG8TOxlE8LVcPNoh3oD6UU9X_f0_uh2IMi4HkV0nNWtTPwZUAPx-Lkyyzu2mGA3gXhlDQwIIpq0OOqfwN6bJssppKeFUTOXsyn7mJrh7F10W6YO8HWtvSqup4mwreCvZBz303Y6T7Y4L4d8pUFkvBqoc7apsE22RGycTBdQU1p6a3Z8LyuUHEe5emhyY/s600/DSC04336.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲內容物一覽</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiZ_K0KfVvkKO1KMSdHRBNXK7IooJmcjcMGHFvYJpDZVu27TOUr_9vX10kzQBJKnvPAnOul5poVFesY7MNTQzuVqHhCHS4OYDVlo_rBpmE6Dqr3c6ku4IBVHpCv6EdAJ10_f0hGvpQ4JbzBQOeWNBPOo4aqqWkn6G2-VSDbeHD3qDlIZXNX2aGJuMWRHE8/s3780/DSC04337.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiZ_K0KfVvkKO1KMSdHRBNXK7IooJmcjcMGHFvYJpDZVu27TOUr_9vX10kzQBJKnvPAnOul5poVFesY7MNTQzuVqHhCHS4OYDVlo_rBpmE6Dqr3c6ku4IBVHpCv6EdAJ10_f0hGvpQ4JbzBQOeWNBPOo4aqqWkn6G2-VSDbeHD3qDlIZXNX2aGJuMWRHE8/s600/DSC04337.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲主要配件就是卡片一包</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh8JPTbf_eKIuQayUUJv0SAkOAN2dvNl1caYDYePJwdEfZDe_VtBwc-CcF-KRYLn1nl9O2rCZCeqO3XLWjtwJ7RIyypy3R4NseGUTpw2YUTmU1Y6y0S0fE3DhEEMdTH3Ir4cDOZkdcGGYs2FL7LVCrRc7MQSwMAHQfEItqsztw4Zw0GKBTeyfxMuxf-80Y/s4672/DSC04338.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh8JPTbf_eKIuQayUUJv0SAkOAN2dvNl1caYDYePJwdEfZDe_VtBwc-CcF-KRYLn1nl9O2rCZCeqO3XLWjtwJ7RIyypy3R4NseGUTpw2YUTmU1Y6y0S0fE3DhEEMdTH3Ir4cDOZkdcGGYs2FL7LVCrRc7MQSwMAHQfEItqsztw4Zw0GKBTeyfxMuxf-80Y/s600/DSC04338.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲有兩張玩家幫助卡跟一疊手牌</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjVfMIIeJQMx5leWBKurWs98VwrFtPrWoNk8xBbA5jQ1LqECRh51QbWHhv4H4UEgwHlAyZZ0HMz8EV-YbVPzAF9m-ex04R9EPggyjYXE_RRGVVbs2TvM_209XtBftgPlbv8VINKP-IJ6q5zCivIR062JBJICMbC2MJwY8z7mzHkwQ-9FgoBNHvFc3yK9ZE/s3312/DSC04339.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjVfMIIeJQMx5leWBKurWs98VwrFtPrWoNk8xBbA5jQ1LqECRh51QbWHhv4H4UEgwHlAyZZ0HMz8EV-YbVPzAF9m-ex04R9EPggyjYXE_RRGVVbs2TvM_209XtBftgPlbv8VINKP-IJ6q5zCivIR062JBJICMbC2MJwY8z7mzHkwQ-9FgoBNHvFc3yK9ZE/s600/DSC04339.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲玩家幫助卡分別是ＮＰＣ，還有福澤一家</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEizl4mmcp8EER3Y0n2E0VcYTZHJb2d_CzD2n5InOx9bLlvHXcdU1bcORpXGikZ1VccsMi-ftKa8cT7vMkwxkLYUcN5Ald-vdlcWGt7a9rr4Iia2GQvz-pfksF3pIluh21VQQCPBDN3YuYCqqzjYtN01dksQumlauVYt6lNBYXXvUhEmhQsGlIEwehV1XXE/s4352/DSC04340.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEizl4mmcp8EER3Y0n2E0VcYTZHJb2d_CzD2n5InOx9bLlvHXcdU1bcORpXGikZ1VccsMi-ftKa8cT7vMkwxkLYUcN5Ald-vdlcWGt7a9rr4Iia2GQvz-pfksF3pIluh21VQQCPBDN3YuYCqqzjYtN01dksQumlauVYt6lNBYXXvUhEmhQsGlIEwehV1XXE/s600/DSC04340.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲福澤家的卡片每張卡都有２張</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjUJ8Y4r8UycGNCnYh7nzxsNXzzse4RUpa60Bi-gok_RRC80ygWhPUbuhl8PJwPhXTlgUaDaQ111lMYCtcyz-6V0G6Z5OrVboEyxfM8PAbDnRZXeNyuQUwq5Y9NRL8tVYv8Y9XvUt5ty0_Z82Aj8diBO3lgiCxTT6yWsIV86wYD_YKsYOdO5KZ_fox4iko/s4317/DSC04342.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjUJ8Y4r8UycGNCnYh7nzxsNXzzse4RUpa60Bi-gok_RRC80ygWhPUbuhl8PJwPhXTlgUaDaQ111lMYCtcyz-6V0G6Z5OrVboEyxfM8PAbDnRZXeNyuQUwq5Y9NRL8tVYv8Y9XvUt5ty0_Z82Aj8diBO3lgiCxTT6yWsIV86wYD_YKsYOdO5KZ_fox4iko/s600/DSC04342.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲ＮＰＣ的中立角色們則是每張卡都只有１張</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEjeQ5l7zhnehKqTVQrvS72sbC9q5LydEZBbyd4Bfpdg7XbpwYvzM6_2vCu-C54OZPMWwRkkhD1Z9h_IL3Ev7uZ2YlNqHBFASwHK-DdaTnSrdw-mkt93TCWfBF4CKwCyAjWfXJWo7ewJPiBL7MZ74WoD8LpuCWpR2KLXgivPoU8VaUZFqpQGWqxhk8uYdsY\"></p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh0hfO-oh1U1rZLrraGg_2mhgV_b1dF81WRNmFLOfmMGAOgYdi0qRA4DrTjd9WGYNQZyFBZp0qZpKaklounBPpYxTxRUYxUXBNGcj5dQfFHw_yf40iuvJrxP1CnIzewCLBJ36D4hssd7K6ua498ld9WgDGFjap7Aqw40ImM6IrPgGNk7npDGqzB7pj9bVs/s4608/DSC04343.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh0hfO-oh1U1rZLrraGg_2mhgV_b1dF81WRNmFLOfmMGAOgYdi0qRA4DrTjd9WGYNQZyFBZp0qZpKaklounBPpYxTxRUYxUXBNGcj5dQfFHw_yf40iuvJrxP1CnIzewCLBJ36D4hssd7K6ua498ld9WgDGFjap7Aqw40ImM6IrPgGNk7npDGqzB7pj9bVs/s600/DSC04343.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲遊戲設置時，我們先將福澤一家各拿出１張～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEghG40inxJSQQ-4TdaMmOjNrDb_Mhz7cf521SHCrWPfSXl5paFHHzS0QxeTgmoQoa5YOM0yh9uXXjLppWDT880ERe5DSALhbix94ZIg4pjdo3zlKCxmsWisPWEGFZg0qjf3qAmLj-7TgNGZBEO72XgRMZRR1JImo_4Z9QXTXDd_Ujx6Dg_rpfBDSSD57c0/s4268/DSC04344.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEghG40inxJSQQ-4TdaMmOjNrDb_Mhz7cf521SHCrWPfSXl5paFHHzS0QxeTgmoQoa5YOM0yh9uXXjLppWDT880ERe5DSALhbix94ZIg4pjdo3zlKCxmsWisPWEGFZg0qjf3qAmLj-7TgNGZBEO72XgRMZRR1JImo_4Z9QXTXDd_Ujx6Dg_rpfBDSSD57c0/s600/DSC04344.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲隨機洗好之後，抽出１張面朝上，１張面朝下</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">（以上圖來說，『福澤家的長女－富士子』被殺死了，旁邊蓋著的那張則是兇手）</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjIZvc1W50D6aO3dP5wUFQC0bRhQRN0Md6Jdhy5G85UJPCzprncW7nOurgdjfXHPCSHOsA-xkOAm6sLhZD_1bcKLW8acy2HIz1I68sOCKxGjcLImVyUHhON9fnjQvrmb2YOOY739t72EVqqpWZy93j-NoNIsoYYVA0WzjF9fcyjLrCkM7KWhAH8iacaSwk/s4812/DSC04345.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjIZvc1W50D6aO3dP5wUFQC0bRhQRN0Md6Jdhy5G85UJPCzprncW7nOurgdjfXHPCSHOsA-xkOAm6sLhZD_1bcKLW8acy2HIz1I68sOCKxGjcLImVyUHhON9fnjQvrmb2YOOY739t72EVqqpWZy93j-NoNIsoYYVA0WzjF9fcyjLrCkM7KWhAH8iacaSwk/s600/DSC04345.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲接著會把剛剛剩下的６張福澤家人卡，以及完整的８張福澤家人卡跟Ｎ張隨機ＮＰＣ角色（根據遊戲人數，查說明書表格）形成牌庫，洗牌之後將所有卡片平均發給每位玩家～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhNdbXdhgSkDeDhRNqQ2yS9CjTgY49oCNfSD8G2jh09B2EIpe8pnFP26iUqfctsO97gZk_yqTNcgjjx9VfjQQrzuEjfKPeh_pC2alXMuIEO_QpS5WZajLDwJ69XBomrpiiEviaY2Jge3q3efQhD5GciH_OvBBF-d3MPnQNog3uGGKhPmFbxxVbuFoRDWDc/s4248/DSC04346.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhNdbXdhgSkDeDhRNqQ2yS9CjTgY49oCNfSD8G2jh09B2EIpe8pnFP26iUqfctsO97gZk_yqTNcgjjx9VfjQQrzuEjfKPeh_pC2alXMuIEO_QpS5WZajLDwJ69XBomrpiiEviaY2Jge3q3efQhD5GciH_OvBBF-d3MPnQNog3uGGKhPmFbxxVbuFoRDWDc/s600/DSC04346.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲輪到你的時候你有三種行動選一個做：</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">１．與右手邊玩家交換一張卡片</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">２．打出一張卡片並執行卡片能力</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">３．猜測凶手身分（直接喊出你懷疑的人，並打開兇手卡自己看），如果猜對，你贏了！遊戲結束；如果猜錯，遊戲繼續進行，但你就不能參與了。</p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhjuQmIwTz4viFidr_DlAdv5tPmKm-1_-YqcV0JxUWqaCxRs4xzLB0k3mFWhWjRhzRg6dA-CC15qTLsg5UCDaG1w4snGC5erg1KEksXGdVXS-qXIgILU0V9rWhFGlDwny1zOzCEWYXJxHhSIIdfgV-vCky-TYIl4yElc77NAn6NvTf0kWLbmMc61dwjP1c/s4928/DSC04347.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhjuQmIwTz4viFidr_DlAdv5tPmKm-1_-YqcV0JxUWqaCxRs4xzLB0k3mFWhWjRhzRg6dA-CC15qTLsg5UCDaG1w4snGC5erg1KEksXGdVXS-qXIgILU0V9rWhFGlDwny1zOzCEWYXJxHhSIIdfgV-vCky-TYIl4yElc77NAn6NvTf0kWLbmMc61dwjP1c/s600/DSC04347.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲隨著遊戲進行，場上會出現更多的被害者，沒錯！這是一樁連續殺人事件～以上圖來說，由於『福澤家的夫人－松子』的２張卡片都已經被打出來了，所以她也被殺死了！此外，有一些ＮＰＣ角色被打出的時候也會立刻死亡（卡片左上角有圖示）。</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">角色的生與死，會影響一些卡片能力的作用，因此可以把場上已經打出的角色分成兩區～此外，已經死掉的福澤家人，也絕對不會是兇手，這是推理時很重要的依據之一～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">遊戲不斷進行，直到有人猜出兇手（該玩家獲勝），或是所有人都猜過一次兇手但都沒猜中（兇手獲勝，所有玩家都輸），遊戲結束～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEgwaHMhRr9BEqbne_uL3byr_6h4d_dPvZgKDQAnMHJfsUc2rnO9pjp_gz5UJdMxXKGvi4ER0b2bI1a-b9EMerP0hAJuJrkMoMQ7ZbtdJY0o_-AEIxjQLt3EZyHqyW61dwO4zM3bPSBbCCDBAEm2xDfz2ui8QkWpzbihDhqJyETPru_qQ7oBoCs7qcuTbTk\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>真相只有一個！</strong></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">《臆斷推理殺人事件：福澤家的落日》是一款日系的推理小品，美術風格與氣氛的營造我蠻喜歡的，而且靠著少少的幾張卡片就可以讓大家嘴砲＋想破頭～雖然說就是簡單的刪去法，但實際玩起來還蠻燒腦的～是一款遊戲體驗蠻不錯的日系推理小品～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">雖然遊戲配件只有卡片，但由於生動的插畫，還有豐富的人物設定，玩起來主題感算是相當不錯～每個人物都有一句形容詞＋一句台詞，還有年紀與更多細節的介紹，所以真的很感謝有中文版可以玩，如果是玩日文版，這些細節玩家們就無法體會到了～以下簡單隨便舉兩個例子：</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">【開始癡呆的彌吉】身為福澤家的大家長，彌吉是６８歲的商業巨頭，蠱惑人心的鬼才。但也已經敗給了年紀，漸漸癡呆了起來。打出卡片之後，所有玩家都跟左手邊的玩家抽１張卡片，但打出彌吉的玩家可以額外再多抽１張。（我不知道啊，我癡呆啦～我剛剛還沒有抽卡片啊，再給我１張啦～）</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">【知道太多的記者】，是３５歲的犬飼修，他的嗅覺很敏銳，但體臭卻很重，目前正因為花粉症而困擾著，一把鼻涕一把眼淚的。手牌在２張以下時才可以打出，選擇一位其他玩家他必須立刻推理犯人，如果該玩家猜中，他立即獲勝；如果他猜錯，他就立刻退出遊戲，並把手牌全部給你～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">以上便是這次的簡單介紹，最後偷偷跟大家說，遊戲的卡片內還有不少八卦可以挖，比方說身為福澤家長女的富士子，居然比福澤家夫人的松子還要大一歲。另外只要稍微算了一下，就會發現松子生竹男的時候才１９歲！當你想罵死老頭彌吉太禽獸的時候，居然發現．．．竹男的生父居然好像不是彌吉！！？？真的是很複雜的一家人～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEi3vi5uxYiZSkNf6zxL6x7a6UG03QA7BWkmQ4CA__CZ8uMiMIfM-MsO_s-c7Wp6UFbGCsPxnveUSJS6-ZbmKZ7ZmTVjU-mjL6c-vOvIPzugmCZ1013bz156I05J_RV0JLAkNOVwQVBW6cq4J9UWMNguoUzzRf0pzTJLtJCwZGsjH4yHzJmAcucljx-ZvXI/s600/DSC04349.JPG\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲遊戲收納照</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh9l5KTRJtB3iAKDGx0pG2Pbb1jPlKW9nOURAROPdVZjbx9zQffQvnM3TJgqgG5-VNgLgpB0onBM9gJM933yvKRrtNXnJkav9QbyhiTYHhWfif-UI6hGU3UHsGB-Q346YT2B14FEA3sgUAWNwviYTd-0GysWJj75xCbqozcxNI9vnt2CrbQTjVeh9BsQK0/s5472/DSC04348.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh9l5KTRJtB3iAKDGx0pG2Pbb1jPlKW9nOURAROPdVZjbx9zQffQvnM3TJgqgG5-VNgLgpB0onBM9gJM933yvKRrtNXnJkav9QbyhiTYHhWfif-UI6hGU3UHsGB-Q346YT2B14FEA3sgUAWNwviYTd-0GysWJj75xCbqozcxNI9vnt2CrbQTjVeh9BsQK0/s600/DSC04348.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p><br></p>', '2024-11-18 10:39:11', '2024-11-18 10:39:11', 1, 'forum-1731897551775-744699741.jpg'),
